1:15:04.127 --> 1:15:07.002
What were you doing
when these kids stole your phone?

1:15:07.043 --> 1:15:08.877
On top of it you have
this stuck up attitude!

1:15:08.918 --> 1:15:10.627
- Go away
- I won't leave you

1:15:10.668 --> 1:15:12.252
Listen to me
Just run away

1:15:12.293 --> 1:15:13.585
- Run outside
- I won't go

1:15:13.627 --> 1:15:15.793
Mess up all my orders
Only plus is your voice!

1:15:15.877 --> 1:15:16.877
I won't go

1:15:16.918 --> 1:15:18.793
You have only 1 minute left

1:15:18.835 --> 1:15:19.835
Decide fast

1:15:19.877 --> 1:15:20.877
Go away from here

1:15:20.918 --> 1:15:23.335
I won't leave you alone

1:15:32.793 --> 1:15:34.043
'What are you doing?'

1:15:34.460 --> 1:15:35.668
'Don't, bro'

1:15:36.884 --> 1:15:38.800
This is what I expected from you!

1:15:40.002 --> 1:15:41.210
Clear out

1:15:41.293 --> 1:15:42.877
I won't leave you

1:15:51.835 --> 1:15:54.168
Annaaaa...!

1:15:55.460 --> 1:15:57.418
Wake up, bro
Get up

1:15:57.460 --> 1:15:59.960
I'm constable Arumugam
Get up, bro

1:16:00.002 --> 1:16:02.668
School starts only at 10'o clock
Why are you waking me-

1:16:02.710 --> 1:16:04.960
We have a problem on hand
Inspector wants to see you

1:16:05.002 --> 1:16:06.835
Why should I meet the inspector?

1:16:06.877 --> 1:16:09.335
Get up, you are sleeping
not realizing it's an emergency

1:16:09.377 --> 1:16:10.752
Okay, I'll get up

1:16:10.793 --> 1:16:12.668
Don't shake me up like a rattle!

1:16:13.127 --> 1:16:14.335
Go, I'll follow

1:16:15.874 --> 1:16:17.082
'I will come'

1:16:18.627 --> 1:16:21.835
"You say you heard a rumor"

1:16:23.627 --> 1:16:25.627
"And it's time I let you know"

1:16:25.788 --> 1:16:27.038
Start the car, quick

1:16:54.460 --> 1:16:59.710
"If delinquents like us lament in pain
will our voice be heard; or is it in vain?"

1:17:00.460 --> 1:17:01.752
'Not too sure, sir'

1:17:01.793 --> 1:17:03.835
'I think they were here
for less than a year'

1:17:04.668 --> 1:17:09.752
"2 innocent boys here
Lost their lives so dear"

1:17:09.793 --> 1:17:13.085
"To reside here or hang by a rope
One and the same without hope"

1:17:13.127 --> 1:17:15.002
'What are you gawking at, huh?'

1:17:15.181 --> 1:17:16.264
Yov! Who are you?

1:17:16.293 --> 1:17:17.502
- Get out
- Sir...sir

1:17:17.585 --> 1:17:19.043
He is our class master

1:17:19.127 --> 1:17:22.002
Oh! You are that master, huh?
First I have to interrogate you

1:17:22.043 --> 1:17:23.335
What did you do?

1:17:23.377 --> 1:17:24.835
This has never happened before

1:17:24.877 --> 1:17:26.335
Did you hit any of the boys?

1:17:26.377 --> 1:17:27.335
Tell me

1:17:27.377 --> 1:17:29.210
Can't you hear me?
Answer, man

1:17:30.668 --> 1:17:32.960
Sir, what is this?

1:17:33.002 --> 1:17:34.752
Not here, I need to
take him for inquiry

1:17:34.835 --> 1:17:36.835
'Get him into our police jeep'

1:17:36.877 --> 1:17:40.127
'Search all the rooms in case
they left any suicide note'

1:17:40.210 --> 1:17:44.668
"We want to reform given a choice
We are good-for-nothing boys"

1:17:45.168 --> 1:17:51.460
"If delinquents like us lament in pain
will our voice be heard; or is it in vain?"

1:17:55.335 --> 1:18:00.960
"If good-for-nothing louts wail
will our voice make justice prevail?"

1:18:03.293 --> 1:18:05.752
'N2 Police Station
Vadaseri'

1:18:14.585 --> 1:18:17.127
Bhavani, can we come with you?

1:18:17.668 --> 1:18:19.918
He has asked me to come
by myself, I can handle it

1:18:19.960 --> 1:18:22.627
What about...that master
who is in police custody?

1:18:25.174 --> 1:18:27.549
I came out of the reformatory 15 years ago

1:18:27.668 --> 1:18:29.585
Reason I've been patient
for the past 5 years

1:18:29.627 --> 1:18:33.293
I wanted to kill these 3 men and
become the president of the Drivers' union

1:18:33.408 --> 1:18:36.199
2 men are dead and gone
This is the last one to go down

1:18:36.233 --> 1:18:37.566
He has sent for me

1:18:38.002 --> 1:18:39.377
Is he my priority?

1:18:40.085 --> 1:18:41.668
Or is this master important?

1:18:41.710 --> 1:18:42.877
He's only important

1:18:43.043 --> 1:18:45.252
- What shall we do with this master?
- I'll handle him

1:18:45.293 --> 1:18:47.168
- Sure?
- No problem

1:18:47.210 --> 1:18:49.085
- Shall I go now?
- I'll go

1:18:50.127 --> 1:18:51.335
Let's go

1:18:57.627 --> 1:18:58.918
Come with me

1:19:06.918 --> 1:19:07.960
Where are you going?

1:19:08.002 --> 1:19:10.418
- 2 minutes, sir
- Quick, sir will be here anytime

1:19:10.585 --> 1:19:12.585
'Are you the mother of
those 2 boys who died?'

1:19:12.627 --> 1:19:14.502
- 'Yes, sir
- Is that so?'

1:19:14.627 --> 1:19:15.960
'Give him all the details'

1:19:16.002 --> 1:19:17.418
Boozed upto your brow, huh?

1:19:17.460 --> 1:19:20.127
- 'Sit outside
- Okay, sir'

1:19:20.918 --> 1:19:23.085
If someone is calling you
10 times from the same #

1:19:23.127 --> 1:19:25.418
...won't it occur to you
it may be a serious problem?

1:19:25.460 --> 1:19:27.668
No, Ch...Charu

1:19:28.085 --> 1:19:29.460
Why are you staring so blankly?

1:19:29.502 --> 1:19:32.293
I was a volunteer in an NGO
before I took up this post here

1:19:32.877 --> 1:19:36.418
Based on a complaint I went
for inspection to that Observation Home

1:19:36.710 --> 1:19:39.085
That's how I befriended those 2 boys

1:19:40.043 --> 1:19:43.043
They told me about the injustice
in that reformatory

1:19:43.127 --> 1:19:45.877
But I couldn't take
any legal action

1:19:45.918 --> 1:19:47.168
So many vile threats

1:19:47.210 --> 1:19:49.960
The only reason I shifted to Chennai
was to handle such cases myself

1:19:50.002 --> 1:19:53.502
I needed to be financially secure
So I took up this lecturer's post

1:19:54.085 --> 1:19:57.668
When you defended the students
my faith was recharged

1:19:58.168 --> 1:20:01.168
I was convinced this flawed system
could be changed for the better

1:20:03.543 --> 1:20:05.460
I forged your signature for this post

1:20:05.502 --> 1:20:07.918
Even for your job
I was the one who applied

1:20:08.043 --> 1:20:09.668
Even the founder is aware of this

1:20:09.710 --> 1:20:11.877
Now I feel that was a big mistake

1:20:13.793 --> 1:20:17.752
If you hadn't come here
at least those 2 boys would be alive

1:20:19.377 --> 1:20:21.335
Now both of them have left us

1:20:21.418 --> 1:20:23.210
How can you defend yourself, sir?

1:20:28.043 --> 1:20:31.877
See, I had no idea whatsoever
No one told me anything

1:20:31.918 --> 1:20:34.043
When have you been
sober enough to understand?

1:20:34.085 --> 1:20:37.168
Have you ever realized anytime
who is talking to you?

1:20:41.043 --> 1:20:43.168
I have my share of personal problems

1:20:43.210 --> 1:20:45.043
I am unable to come out of it

1:20:45.793 --> 1:20:46.918
I can't

1:20:47.627 --> 1:20:48.835
...cry

1:20:49.585 --> 1:20:52.585
I can't cry, I can't sleep
at night either, that's why

1:20:55.543 --> 1:20:56.710
I drink

1:20:56.793 --> 1:21:00.335
I swear I never thought
it would be this horrific

1:21:00.768 --> 1:21:03.143
Oh! You can never cry, right?

1:21:03.710 --> 1:21:05.710
'I can't understand
Tell me without crying'

1:21:05.752 --> 1:21:06.752
Charu, where are yo-

1:21:06.793 --> 1:21:09.793
- Were your boys into drugs?
- I never thought I would see them dead

1:21:09.835 --> 1:21:12.627
This is the lady who gave birth
to those boys who are dead now

1:21:12.668 --> 1:21:14.085
I had reassured her

1:21:14.127 --> 1:21:15.293
A master will come

1:21:15.335 --> 1:21:17.335
'He will save your boys'

1:21:17.960 --> 1:21:22.293
Both my sons are very fond of each other
They stick together like glue

1:21:22.960 --> 1:21:25.460
My eldest told me
just last week

1:21:25.502 --> 1:21:29.085
'Let my younger brother study
I'll find some job to support us'

1:21:29.127 --> 1:21:31.127
'A master was coming he said'

1:21:31.168 --> 1:21:33.793
He was sure they will be rescued

1:21:33.918 --> 1:21:35.877
But no one came

1:21:36.050 --> 1:21:39.092
'My entire lineage has snapped'

1:21:39.585 --> 1:21:41.377
Yov! Where are you?

1:21:41.543 --> 1:21:42.710
Hurry up

1:21:43.418 --> 1:21:44.710
'Listen to him'

1:21:44.835 --> 1:21:46.085
Bring your wife

1:21:46.293 --> 1:21:48.793
- Yov! Come here
- You can go

1:21:49.210 --> 1:21:50.877
'He has gone back to his old ways'

1:21:50.918 --> 1:21:52.710
- Sir
- Who are they?

1:21:53.127 --> 1:21:55.418
She is that master's colleague it seems

1:21:55.460 --> 1:21:57.460
Pack them all off and
move that master to the cell

1:21:57.502 --> 1:21:58.460
Okay, sir

1:21:58.502 --> 1:22:00.793
Yov! Clear the other cases
out of the station

1:22:00.835 --> 1:22:01.835
Okay, sir

1:22:01.877 --> 1:22:03.502
'What will I do now?'

1:22:04.293 --> 1:22:05.918
'How will I live without them?'

1:22:05.960 --> 1:22:07.710
'Even now you're so hard hearted?'

1:22:07.752 --> 1:22:10.002
Your eyes won't shed tears
till the day you die

1:22:10.181 --> 1:22:11.418
Get even more sloshed

1:22:11.460 --> 1:22:13.918
'Why are you lamenting here?
Shut up now'

1:22:13.960 --> 1:22:15.210
I said shut up

1:22:15.710 --> 1:22:18.668
Do I have to repeat myself?
Clear this place now, madam

1:22:18.710 --> 1:22:19.793
Clear out

1:22:20.002 --> 1:22:21.127
Come with me, sir

1:22:21.877 --> 1:22:22.960
I swear-

1:22:23.002 --> 1:22:25.460
Come along, sir
Standing rooted to the spot

1:22:25.502 --> 1:22:27.543
I swear I didn't expect any of this

1:22:27.585 --> 1:22:30.585
Don't forget you are also responsible
for the death of those 2 boys

1:22:30.627 --> 1:22:32.293
Convey my apologies to their mother

1:22:32.335 --> 1:22:34.918
You are taking undue advantage
of the respect I'm giving you

1:22:34.960 --> 1:22:37.293
Don't make me lose my temper
Stand right there

1:22:37.668 --> 1:22:40.127
I sacrificed my children
in such an awful unjust way

1:22:40.168 --> 1:22:41.752
'Hey! Come here'

1:22:42.043 --> 1:22:45.043
Sir, get some repellent
Mosquitoes are lifting us midair!

1:22:52.168 --> 1:22:53.293
'Go inside'

1:23:19.460 --> 1:23:21.043
Listen, Bhavani

1:23:21.127 --> 1:23:25.293
Only you and I are left to contest
the Lorry Drivers' Union election

1:23:25.377 --> 1:23:27.043
I have to win unopposed

1:23:27.085 --> 1:23:28.627
'Looks like it may rain'

1:23:28.668 --> 1:23:30.460
Can we have tea
and then discuss?

1:23:39.543 --> 1:23:40.752
[sniffles]

1:23:57.710 --> 1:24:00.418
'Master, my name is Sabari'

1:24:00.572 --> 1:24:02.322
'My elder brother is Manikandan'

1:24:02.355 --> 1:24:06.314
'He stole from a bakery for my sake
because I was starving'

1:24:06.710 --> 1:24:10.460
'But they foisted some other case
on us and brought us here'

1:24:10.752 --> 1:24:12.752
'Everything is wrong here, master'

1:24:13.043 --> 1:24:14.877
'They thrash us mercilessly'

1:24:14.918 --> 1:24:17.043
'They stuff some powder into our mouths'

1:24:17.627 --> 1:24:21.460
'Immediately even our teeth
start shivering, master'

1:24:21.835 --> 1:24:24.127
'Don't know if it is day or night'

1:24:24.918 --> 1:24:28.002
'We put up with all this
thinking it is for a short period'

1:24:28.043 --> 1:24:29.668
'Now when we are
about to be released'

1:24:29.710 --> 1:24:32.210
'...they want us to surrender
for some other murder case'

1:24:32.642 --> 1:24:35.377
'Otherwise they are threatening
to kill our mother, master'

1:24:35.418 --> 1:24:40.002
'Charu akka assured us you will come
and be our savior, rescue us'

1:24:40.869 --> 1:24:42.543
'Please save us, master'

1:24:43.127 --> 1:24:44.627
'Our poor mother'

1:24:44.668 --> 1:24:46.275
'She is all alone'

1:24:46.342 --> 1:24:48.092
'Crying nonstop daily'

1:24:48.501 --> 1:24:50.584
'I can't cry anymore, master'

1:24:50.918 --> 1:24:53.585
'Please, brother
Rescue us from this hell'

1:24:53.858 --> 1:24:55.900
'I am begging you, anna'

1:25:16.252 --> 1:25:17.252
Go ahead

1:25:18.210 --> 1:25:19.710
I told you, Bhavani

1:25:19.918 --> 1:25:21.210
I want to win unopposed

1:25:21.293 --> 1:25:23.668
I called you here
to arrive at a compromise

1:25:23.710 --> 1:25:25.418
But still I can't trust you

1:25:26.377 --> 1:25:31.085
You'll take any kind of cruel measure
using those juvenile delinquents

1:25:31.252 --> 1:25:36.168
Should I step out of my house daily
with fear in every breath I exhale?

1:25:38.168 --> 1:25:39.127
That is why-

1:25:39.168 --> 1:25:42.168
Did you call me here
planning to kill me?

1:25:44.502 --> 1:25:45.627
You-

1:25:45.710 --> 1:25:47.835
You call someone
with a plan to kill him

1:25:47.877 --> 1:25:50.585
Treat him royally like a guest
and offer him hot tea

1:25:50.627 --> 1:25:53.668
You're the only man who
asked me for permission to kill

1:25:53.710 --> 1:25:55.710
Instead you could have-

1:25:55.752 --> 1:25:59.293
Putting you on a pedestal, I wanted to
fix an auspicious day to finish you off

1:25:59.335 --> 1:26:01.585
I need my brain examined!

1:26:03.710 --> 1:26:05.210
'Hey! Wait'

1:26:06.043 --> 1:26:07.793
I'll give you 2 minutes

1:26:09.306 --> 1:26:12.347
Kill me and then save
your men and yourself

1:26:34.252 --> 1:26:35.502
'Hurry up'

1:26:37.668 --> 1:26:40.085
Do you need an army
to bash up 1 man?

1:26:40.418 --> 1:26:41.752
Open the door first

1:27:23.752 --> 1:27:25.502
Hey, he is a master
Watch your blows

1:27:25.543 --> 1:27:26.793
You have only 10 minutes

1:27:26.835 --> 1:27:28.543
Come out without too much damage

1:27:29.710 --> 1:27:31.043
Turn the other way

1:27:34.335 --> 1:27:35.627
Murali, come

1:27:35.668 --> 1:27:37.002
Switch it off and come

1:28:01.710 --> 1:28:04.168
Even if you are reborn
pray I don't set eyes on you!

1:28:04.210 --> 1:28:05.835
Don't, Bhavani

1:28:15.752 --> 1:28:17.335
Wonder what their plan is!

1:28:17.939 --> 1:28:21.230
Master, my boss has
given you a bus ticket

1:28:21.293 --> 1:28:23.627
'Luxury bus
Air-condition sleeper'

1:28:23.668 --> 1:28:26.127
Leave tonight, you'll reach
your hometown in the morning

1:28:26.710 --> 1:28:27.793
Got it into your head?

1:28:27.835 --> 1:28:29.752
'If you stubbornly refuse'

1:28:29.793 --> 1:28:31.627
You saw the 2 boys
hanging from the roof?

1:28:31.668 --> 1:28:33.210
You'll be next

1:28:34.080 --> 1:28:35.460
I'm talking to you

1:28:35.502 --> 1:28:37.168
Is that a love letter in your hand?

1:28:39.210 --> 1:28:41.335
Sabari, Manikandan

1:28:41.418 --> 1:28:43.752
[reading under his breath]

1:28:44.168 --> 1:28:48.168
Refusing to surrender in the murder case
and ended up dead, those 2 tramps-

1:29:35.210 --> 1:29:37.752
Sir, the noise is too loud

1:29:39.293 --> 1:29:40.793
Ignore, we'll handle it

1:30:18.210 --> 1:30:19.960
Sir, the noise is ear-splitting

1:30:20.710 --> 1:30:22.210
- Go in and check
- Okay

1:30:42.085 --> 1:30:44.418
'Stab him and rip him apart'

1:30:51.002 --> 1:30:52.043
Sir?

1:30:52.377 --> 1:30:55.043
They may kill that master
Please come here, sir

1:31:03.210 --> 1:31:04.460
Hey Soundar!

1:31:09.085 --> 1:31:10.710
Open the damn door

1:31:21.168 --> 1:31:22.543
Soundar

1:31:43.127 --> 1:31:44.835
- Tell me
- BHAVANI!

1:31:45.835 --> 1:31:47.877
The master-

1:31:55.210 --> 1:31:56.627
Who are you?

1:31:57.002 --> 1:31:59.168
Who is behind this?
What is your motive?

1:31:59.210 --> 1:32:02.543
Why do you use these innocent boys?
I don't know any of this

1:32:03.752 --> 1:32:05.210
But I will find out

1:32:05.918 --> 1:32:08.877
'Hiding behind these young boys and
framing them, neck deep in crime'

1:32:08.918 --> 1:32:11.085
I will catch those sissy fellows

1:32:12.460 --> 1:32:15.543
I'll hunt high and low, find you
and stand right in front of you

1:32:16.085 --> 1:32:17.377
I will-

1:32:20.960 --> 1:32:25.168
I will make you answer
for the death of those 2 boys

1:32:26.877 --> 1:32:28.002
Master

1:32:29.002 --> 1:32:31.918
Whatever I'm about to say
is nothing new for you

1:32:33.095 --> 1:32:35.261
Still I'll say it
and you listen

1:32:38.358 --> 1:32:39.483
I'm waiting!

1:32:41.460 --> 1:32:43.460
[confident laughter]

1:32:44.502 --> 1:32:45.502
Wait, I say

1:32:45.543 --> 1:32:46.835
I will meet you face to face

1:32:46.877 --> 1:32:48.210
"He stands for powerful victory"

1:32:48.285 --> 1:32:49.702
- "Who is he?
- Thalapathy...!"

1:33:07.269 --> 1:33:09.168
'Das, I'm very scared'

1:33:09.210 --> 1:33:11.543
'He is back again
Is there no one to save me?'

1:33:11.585 --> 1:33:13.127
'Aiyaiyo!'

1:33:13.168 --> 1:33:15.752
"Don't spoil for a fight unnecessarily"

1:33:15.793 --> 1:33:18.918
"If you give us hell foolhardily
a stone will split your skull speedily"

1:33:18.960 --> 1:33:21.543
Master, you've been staring
at the rope for a long time?

1:33:21.585 --> 1:33:22.960
Want to play on it as a swing?

1:33:23.002 --> 1:33:24.460
What is that famous song of his?

1:33:24.543 --> 1:33:26.460
Let me tell a 'kutti' story

1:33:26.509 --> 1:33:28.050
Hey chee chee!
Not short, da

1:33:28.085 --> 1:33:29.377
Saaaad story!

1:33:29.511 --> 1:33:31.585
"Let me tell a sad story"

1:33:31.627 --> 1:33:34.335
"Zip lip, or slip
Skip and trip"

1:33:34.377 --> 1:33:36.585
"Chillax, master!"

1:33:38.502 --> 1:33:40.418
"Take a deep breath, master"

1:33:40.460 --> 1:33:42.335
Hey master!

1:33:42.377 --> 1:33:44.627
"Cheers to your beers!"

1:33:51.793 --> 1:33:55.168
'Night and day, the oldest youngster
to the youngest boy, all are doped'

1:33:55.210 --> 1:33:58.043
'When they are intoxicated
they are not in control of their senses'

1:33:58.085 --> 1:34:00.502
'Both have plenty of
criminal cases against them'

1:34:00.543 --> 1:34:02.085
'2 boys who died are sheer poison'

1:34:02.127 --> 1:34:04.127
'Both must have died
when totally tanked, sir'

1:34:04.168 --> 1:34:06.793
'They won't toe the line with
their parents or with our rules'

1:34:06.835 --> 1:34:08.627
They are arrogant boys
who insist their word is law

1:34:08.668 --> 1:34:11.293
'There are 10-12 year olds
with all kinds of diseases here, sir'

1:34:11.335 --> 1:34:12.502
All dazed and doped

1:34:12.543 --> 1:34:15.460
Who told you they were
good-for-nothing boys?

1:34:15.502 --> 1:34:17.252
Both are 24 carat gold, sir

1:34:17.293 --> 1:34:19.460
Both those boys who died

1:34:19.502 --> 1:34:22.043
They called a girl I know
on the night they died

1:34:22.085 --> 1:34:23.877
You mean Charu?

1:34:23.918 --> 1:34:25.168
Yes, Charu

1:34:25.252 --> 1:34:28.585
I know Charu, I also know
who killed those 2 boys

1:34:28.627 --> 1:34:30.335
We have tried our level best

1:34:30.377 --> 1:34:33.585
But we are unable to stop
the dope and booze supply

1:34:33.627 --> 1:34:36.502
How can drugs enter the premises
without your knowledge, sir?

1:34:37.652 --> 1:34:40.548
They have so many routes to supply, sir

1:34:40.604 --> 1:34:42.354
Without the wardens' support

1:34:42.395 --> 1:34:44.354
'...nothing can be brought in, sir'

1:34:44.395 --> 1:34:47.770
As per our rule book, no violence on
our boys who are all below 18 here

1:34:47.812 --> 1:34:50.229
Using that as an excuse
they will bring the roof down!

1:34:50.270 --> 1:34:52.104
Presuming others' fears are their plus

1:34:52.145 --> 1:34:54.229
...these are riff-raffs
who rule the roost

1:34:54.979 --> 1:34:57.895
Poor chaps! Trapped for life
caught in Bhavani's web

1:34:58.858 --> 1:35:00.150
Who is Bhavani?

1:35:00.520 --> 1:35:01.437
Beast!

1:35:01.479 --> 1:35:04.354
- Bhava...Bhavani?
- Don't know anyone by that name

1:35:08.759 --> 1:35:11.395
Sir, don't simply keep asking questions

1:35:11.437 --> 1:35:14.062
You got any other work,
carry on, okay?

1:35:14.104 --> 1:35:15.312
See you, sir?

1:35:15.354 --> 1:35:16.729
Let's go

1:35:45.229 --> 1:35:49.062
'Teachers who came here earlier to reform
these boys, giving priority to their family'

1:35:49.104 --> 1:35:51.354
...would have made a hasty retreat

1:35:51.812 --> 1:35:53.645
But my story is completely different

1:35:54.437 --> 1:35:56.312
I have no one to call my own, sir

1:35:57.354 --> 1:36:01.354
'The day I saw those 2 boys
hang right in front of my eyes'

1:36:02.479 --> 1:36:04.145
Their eyes bulging

1:36:04.770 --> 1:36:06.395
Tongues sticking out

1:36:07.479 --> 1:36:08.729
I died, sir

1:36:12.145 --> 1:36:13.395
If you can help me

1:36:13.437 --> 1:36:15.979
I will change this place and
bring order and fair play here

1:36:17.520 --> 1:36:20.354
Whatever hardship comes my way
I don't care even if I lose my life

1:36:20.395 --> 1:36:21.520
"My life's breath"

1:36:21.562 --> 1:36:22.604
I have no problem, sir

1:36:22.645 --> 1:36:26.437
If you stick to rules & regulations here,
even move heaven and earth legally

1:36:26.479 --> 1:36:27.979
I will back you up 100%, sir

1:36:28.020 --> 1:36:31.645
"High time I stop needing a high from you"

1:36:32.354 --> 1:36:38.187
"Enough of (s)tumbling thanks to you!"

1:36:38.847 --> 1:36:43.722
"Today my troubled times will heal anew"

1:36:44.979 --> 1:36:48.062
"Enough of being sloshed night & day
Get it out of your system today"

1:36:48.104 --> 1:36:51.270
"Enough of gifting yourself strife
Switch off this dizzying life"

1:36:51.312 --> 1:36:54.354
"No more booze to give a kick
Quit now, double quick"

1:36:54.395 --> 1:36:57.687
"Break the bottles, you surely should
Trash them for your own good"

1:36:57.729 --> 1:37:02.187
"Enough of being drunk as a skunk
Get it out of your system as junk"

1:37:02.229 --> 1:37:03.812
Forgive me, ma

1:37:03.854 --> 1:37:06.729
"No more daily booze session
Quit this deadly addiction"

1:37:06.812 --> 1:37:09.979
"Break this habit, begin life anew
Trash the bottles now, dude"

1:37:10.020 --> 1:37:12.937
"Enough of this, night & day
Get it out of your system today"

1:37:12.979 --> 1:37:15.979
"Enough of this dependence
Switch off without a fuss"

1:37:16.020 --> 1:37:19.187
"Enough of being a slave to craving
Quit drinking; no more depraving"

1:37:19.229 --> 1:37:23.437
"Break the bottles and the habit
Trash them for your own benefit"

1:37:46.887 --> 1:37:48.221
You got me wrong, Bhavani

1:37:48.239 --> 1:37:49.739
Ever since Gurumurthy died

1:37:49.787 --> 1:37:52.037
...everyone is scared
to contest for that post

1:37:52.645 --> 1:37:54.312
I've spoken to the district councillor

1:37:54.354 --> 1:37:55.562
In another 10 days

1:37:55.604 --> 1:37:57.729
...it will be announced
you won unopposed

1:37:57.770 --> 1:37:58.812
Come here

1:37:59.437 --> 1:38:01.604
Bro, she is the one
putting a spoke in the wheel

1:38:01.645 --> 1:38:04.270
She registered the case it seems
Our boys sent her photo just now

1:38:04.312 --> 1:38:05.812
What should we do with her?

1:38:05.854 --> 1:38:07.687
Can't you handle a female?

1:38:08.187 --> 1:38:10.729
As if you need a priest to choose
an auspicious time! Get lost!

1:38:11.980 --> 1:38:14.812
Bhavani, even if someone else
occupies this post as union leader

1:38:14.854 --> 1:38:18.270
Anyway whatever you say will be law
Then why aspire for this post?

1:38:18.312 --> 1:38:20.854
Fear stemming out of murder is short lived

1:38:20.937 --> 1:38:24.395
But fear derived from a post of power
and authority lasts a lifetime, right?

1:38:25.062 --> 1:38:26.770
After this I'm entering politics

1:38:27.270 --> 1:38:29.770
Don't know how many heads will roll
to make that dream come true

1:38:29.812 --> 1:38:31.895
- I don't get it, Bhavani
- All God's will

1:38:31.979 --> 1:38:33.812
Our boys will shoulder the sin

1:38:43.187 --> 1:38:46.145
"They call me master
Changes will happen faster"

1:39:19.354 --> 1:39:20.395
Hey master!

1:39:20.437 --> 1:39:22.812
- 'Looking tip-top like a new groom?
- Correct, man'

1:39:22.895 --> 1:39:24.270
He looks different, right?

1:39:24.312 --> 1:39:26.354
'Master is in a mood
to teach us a lesson'

1:39:26.395 --> 1:39:27.812
Do you think he's married?

1:39:27.854 --> 1:39:29.354
'If he was married'

1:39:29.395 --> 1:39:30.895
And if his wife looks hot

1:39:30.937 --> 1:39:32.479
Soooper, no?!

1:39:33.270 --> 1:39:35.187
All of you stand height-wise

1:39:35.979 --> 1:39:37.520
Shorter ones in front

1:39:37.562 --> 1:39:39.562
Taller ones back row
Come on, fast

1:39:39.604 --> 1:39:43.145
If you come clean shaven and yell
you think we'll get scared?

1:39:43.187 --> 1:39:46.354
- 'Move on to your next job
- At least pretend to be scared'

1:39:46.395 --> 1:39:47.604
Poor master!

1:39:47.645 --> 1:39:49.520
Let me repeat

1:39:49.562 --> 1:39:50.854
Fall in line
Stand height-wise

1:39:50.895 --> 1:39:54.979
Master, don't judge a book by its cover
Instead of height try weight as a measure

1:39:55.020 --> 1:39:56.729
This chap like a buffalo here

1:39:56.770 --> 1:39:58.770
'Pickpocket case
Real pipsqueak'

1:39:58.812 --> 1:40:01.562
But our little black ant
had the guts to kill

1:40:01.604 --> 1:40:03.562
Cut above the rest
Then who has more weightage?

1:40:03.604 --> 1:40:05.395
What is your name?

1:40:05.437 --> 1:40:07.437
You heard me?
What is your name?

1:40:07.479 --> 1:40:09.312
Master, you can't lay a finger on us

1:40:09.354 --> 1:40:10.604
Know that, right?

1:40:10.645 --> 1:40:11.645
'Sirrrrr'

1:40:11.979 --> 1:40:13.895
You can't hit the boys

1:40:13.937 --> 1:40:14.979
Rules

1:40:15.729 --> 1:40:18.770
'Don't hit them and
get caught unnecessarily'

1:40:19.604 --> 1:40:22.937
'Like a new starched shirt,
sir is all stiff and spruced up'

1:40:22.979 --> 1:40:24.437
"Master's raid, be ready"

1:40:24.479 --> 1:40:26.562
"A-Aa-E-Ee, A-B-C-D
This is our time, buddy"

1:40:26.604 --> 1:40:28.395
"Come, brother, sure and steady"

1:40:32.395 --> 1:40:34.479
It is wrong only if I bash up the boys?

1:40:34.520 --> 1:40:35.604
Yes

1:40:38.729 --> 1:40:41.979
"World famous local master
will bash up any lowlife gangster"

1:40:42.020 --> 1:40:45.395
"His cane will speak loud and clear
To reform a rowdy, law will persevere"

1:40:45.437 --> 1:40:48.645
"If you come in to commit a crime
Master's raid will give you a hard time"

1:40:48.687 --> 1:40:50.145
"Master's raid
Pain postpaid"

1:40:50.229 --> 1:40:52.437
"Don't buy trouble for a fee
Turn your back and flee"

1:40:52.479 --> 1:40:53.979
Why are you hitting us, sir?

1:40:54.020 --> 1:40:55.854
As master, think you can
get away hitting us?

1:40:55.895 --> 1:40:57.270
'We are also wardens here'

1:40:57.312 --> 1:41:00.229
We told you not to hit the boys
So why are you caning us?

1:41:00.270 --> 1:41:02.520
"Don't run over him and look the other way"

1:41:02.562 --> 1:41:04.645
"Don't get into his bad books, stay away"

1:41:04.687 --> 1:41:07.770
"Master's raid, no warranty
Pain 100% guarantee"

1:41:07.812 --> 1:41:09.770
It hurts, sir
Please don't hit

1:41:09.812 --> 1:41:12.562
Sir, I'm going to Sabarimala
I have taken the 48 days vow

1:41:12.621 --> 1:41:16.163
Why? What happened to your devotion
when you were peddling drugs?

1:41:16.229 --> 1:41:19.645
"He'll even the score and more
His blows blast fireworks encore"

1:41:19.687 --> 1:41:21.062
"Who is the master?
Commander!"

1:41:21.104 --> 1:41:22.645
"24 carat gold is he
Lion king royalty"

1:41:22.687 --> 1:41:24.354
"Move aside
Watch his stride"

1:41:24.437 --> 1:41:26.104
"Shut the gate, dude"

1:41:41.937 --> 1:41:43.145
- Name?
- Bharath

1:41:43.187 --> 1:41:44.437
- Sibi
- Karuppusami

1:41:44.479 --> 1:41:45.562
- Dhanus
- 'Udaya'

1:41:45.604 --> 1:41:46.604
- 'Venkatesh
- Stephen'

1:41:46.645 --> 1:41:47.645
'Pencil'

1:41:47.687 --> 1:41:50.104
Inspection it seems
All of you line up to one side

1:41:50.145 --> 1:41:52.770
"He will take law into his hand
When discipline fails to stand"

1:41:52.812 --> 1:41:54.729
"Master's raid will be well planned"

1:41:54.770 --> 1:41:57.104
"When he uses his soft voice
Obey his rules, dear boys"

1:41:57.145 --> 1:41:59.395
"If you defy however slight
his cane will hug you tight"

1:41:59.437 --> 1:42:01.479
"Don't create a ruckus
His warning smile is dangerous"

1:42:01.520 --> 1:42:03.645
"Accept your mistake, bro
he will then let you go"

1:42:03.687 --> 1:42:04.604
Good boy!

1:42:04.645 --> 1:42:06.687
"What was that noise, lad?
Your nose is bleeding bad"

1:42:06.729 --> 1:42:09.020
"Wherever you hide, dude
master's eyes will find you"

1:42:09.062 --> 1:42:11.354
"Listen to master's advice
you'll be wealthy and wise"

1:42:11.395 --> 1:42:13.895
"If you act smart anymore
time to kneel on the floor"

1:42:33.062 --> 1:42:35.104
"Don't stand and stare
Don't get caught again, beware"

1:42:35.145 --> 1:42:38.104
"Hit him once, you are out cold
He will retaliate multifold"

1:42:38.812 --> 1:42:40.812
"Don't turn a blind eye
to a crime on the roadside"

1:42:40.854 --> 1:42:43.104
"Says 'Thirukkural' wisely
Don't chicken out and flee"

1:42:43.145 --> 1:42:45.104
"My followers devotedly
Will be true wholeheartedly"

1:42:45.187 --> 1:42:47.312
"Without discrimination
of caste, race, religion"

1:42:47.354 --> 1:42:48.854
"Apple of our eye is our nation"

1:42:48.895 --> 1:42:53.187
"We were patient till now; simply
But we will retaliate; world war 3"

1:42:53.229 --> 1:42:55.854
"Continents will quake & quiver
Nonentities will shake & shiver"

1:42:55.895 --> 1:42:57.229
"His entry is power
Loud & clear"

1:42:57.270 --> 1:42:58.312
"Who is he?
Thalapathy"

1:42:58.354 --> 1:43:00.104
"24 carat gold is he
Lion king royalty"

1:43:00.187 --> 1:43:02.270
"Move aside, dude
Beast mode"

1:43:04.854 --> 1:43:07.270
'Master, my name is Sabari
My anna's name is Manikandan'

1:43:07.312 --> 1:43:09.062
'My brother stole from
a bakery for my sake'

1:43:09.104 --> 1:43:10.520
'But they foisted another case-'

1:43:10.562 --> 1:43:12.729
'Bhavani, that master is
acting too big for his boots'

1:43:12.770 --> 1:43:14.062
'He bashed up the wardens'

1:43:14.104 --> 1:43:17.562
'He raided the premises and burnt
all the drugs, dopes and phones'

1:43:17.645 --> 1:43:19.395
'What to do with him now?'

1:43:23.562 --> 1:43:25.895
How did a master get to be so gutsy?

1:43:29.645 --> 1:43:32.437
Find out who is backing him up

1:43:40.395 --> 1:43:41.979
Let's get to work

1:43:51.645 --> 1:43:53.812
"Don't stand and stare
Don't get caught again, beware"

1:43:53.854 --> 1:43:56.770
"Hit him once, you are out cold
He will retaliate multifold"

1:43:57.395 --> 1:44:00.062
"Won't turn a blind eye
to a crime on the roadside"

1:44:00.104 --> 1:44:01.604
My dear angels!

1:44:01.645 --> 1:44:03.062
Can you give us a hand?

1:44:03.104 --> 1:44:05.645
"Without discrimination
of caste, race, religion"

1:44:05.687 --> 1:44:07.354
"Apple of our eye is our nation"

1:44:07.395 --> 1:44:11.854
"We were patient till now; seriously
Reign of terror; world war 3"

1:44:11.895 --> 1:44:14.520
"Continents will quake & quiver
Nonentities will shake & shiver"

1:44:14.562 --> 1:44:15.645
"Master spells power"

1:44:15.687 --> 1:44:16.645
Take your hands off

1:44:16.687 --> 1:44:18.479
"24 carat gold is he
Lion king royalty"

1:44:18.520 --> 1:44:20.354
"Move aside, dude
Beast mode"

1:44:22.729 --> 1:44:24.854
Master, you had your way, eh?

1:44:24.895 --> 1:44:26.604
You can trim my hair
or tonsure my head

1:44:26.645 --> 1:44:29.229
Beware of my leader Undiyal
Try your tricks on him

1:44:29.270 --> 1:44:30.395
'Undiyal, listen to me'

1:44:30.437 --> 1:44:32.562
- Don't go there, go to your block
- Shut up, warden

1:44:32.645 --> 1:44:33.979
- Vanakkam, boss
- Morning, bro

1:44:34.020 --> 1:44:36.187
Who had the guts to
lay a finger on our hair?

1:44:36.229 --> 1:44:38.437
Is there a rule on
the long and short of it?

1:44:38.479 --> 1:44:40.812
Master, do you know the rules or not?

1:44:40.854 --> 1:44:43.187
You are having a free hand
with everyone's heads

1:44:44.395 --> 1:44:45.562
Master

1:44:45.604 --> 1:44:47.312
Let go of me, master

1:44:50.270 --> 1:44:52.479
You don't know whom
you're pitting your wits against

1:44:52.520 --> 1:44:54.312
You will regret what you're doing

1:44:54.354 --> 1:44:56.229
"Master's raid
Pain post paid"

1:44:56.270 --> 1:44:58.562
"Don't get into strife
Run for your life"

1:44:58.604 --> 1:45:00.437
"When he uses his soft voice"

1:45:00.520 --> 1:45:02.104
Gawd! You're scaring me!

1:45:02.145 --> 1:45:03.312
- Hey Dheena
- 'Sir'

1:45:03.354 --> 1:45:04.604
Let it be a close cut

1:45:04.645 --> 1:45:05.812
"Master raid"

1:45:05.854 --> 1:45:08.395
"Don't run over him and look the other way"

1:45:08.437 --> 1:45:10.562
"Don't get into his bad books, stay away"

1:45:10.604 --> 1:45:12.062
"Master's raid
All crimes waylaid"

1:45:12.104 --> 1:45:13.229
"Master's raid, da!"

1:45:13.312 --> 1:45:15.687
"A-Aa-E-Ee, A-B-C-D
This is our time, buddy"

1:45:15.729 --> 1:45:18.229
"Bro, good morning
Master's raid in full swing"

1:45:20.354 --> 1:45:22.645
Next week will be
back to square one

1:45:22.687 --> 1:45:24.854
You can come back
and scrub it again, okay?

1:45:24.895 --> 1:45:26.062
Bye, sweetheart

1:45:26.104 --> 1:45:28.979
I've never seen such bad
nicotine stains at so young an age, JD

1:45:29.020 --> 1:45:31.020
Prise open their mouth
it's like a cigarette shop!

1:45:31.062 --> 1:45:34.395
'I have collected cavity samples
from the 6 boys you mentioned'

1:45:34.437 --> 1:45:37.062
- How long will it take?
- I'll let you know in 1 or 2 days

1:45:37.104 --> 1:45:38.354
Thanks, Madhi

1:45:39.788 --> 1:45:42.020
He left me with a half shaved
moustache and beard

1:45:42.062 --> 1:45:43.562
Such a disgrace!

1:45:43.710 --> 1:45:45.229
I feel like I am naked!

1:45:45.270 --> 1:45:46.645
I'm so mad I feel like sta-

1:45:46.687 --> 1:45:48.354
'I feel like stabbing him right now'

1:45:48.395 --> 1:45:50.854
When you get your hands dirty
enemies will come and go

1:45:50.895 --> 1:45:54.229
If we rage like a mad bull against every
single enemy, our life will be ruined

1:45:54.687 --> 1:45:56.145
Handle him with patience

1:45:56.187 --> 1:45:57.937
'Make him run in all 4 directions'

1:45:57.979 --> 1:45:59.562
Don't let him sleep

1:45:59.645 --> 1:46:01.645
- Torture him mentally
- Fine

1:46:01.687 --> 1:46:03.187
- 'Hey-'
- I'll tackle him

1:46:22.104 --> 1:46:24.020
[overlap of angry voices]

1:46:38.520 --> 1:46:40.854
'Listen to me
I'm telling you boys'

1:46:40.937 --> 1:46:42.395
'Listen to me'

1:46:42.437 --> 1:46:43.562
'Wait, da'

1:46:43.604 --> 1:46:45.312
- What happened?
- Sir, I don't know

1:46:45.354 --> 1:46:47.270
They just started a brawl
and hit each other

1:46:47.312 --> 1:46:49.312
Back door is open in A block
What to do now?

1:46:49.354 --> 1:46:50.895
Go look for the key

1:46:50.937 --> 1:46:52.020
Hurry up

1:46:52.062 --> 1:46:53.104
Quick, man

1:46:53.145 --> 1:46:55.062
Don't let anyone out
Lock them up in the class

1:46:55.104 --> 1:46:56.645
- Okay, bro
- Give me the torch

1:46:56.687 --> 1:46:58.437
'You'll get it from me'

1:47:09.645 --> 1:47:11.104
Get lost!

1:47:38.604 --> 1:47:39.687
Hello, bro

1:47:39.729 --> 1:47:42.187
- 'Yes, tell me'
- None of our boys are missing I hope

1:47:42.270 --> 1:47:44.854
Bro, head count is correct 63

1:47:44.895 --> 1:47:46.770
'Not one of them is missing'

1:47:47.354 --> 1:47:49.604
'They came from outside for sure'

1:48:19.145 --> 1:48:20.604
'Aiyo! It's burning!'

1:48:22.562 --> 1:48:24.104
Aiyo!

1:48:26.479 --> 1:48:28.479
You're hurting me

1:48:32.229 --> 1:48:34.604
Aiyaiyo! Bala

1:48:34.687 --> 1:48:36.562
'What happened to you?'

1:48:37.312 --> 1:48:39.020
'You messed up my face, right?'

1:48:39.062 --> 1:48:40.270
'Go, collect your mess'

1:48:40.312 --> 1:48:42.062
'This is just the beginning, master'

1:48:42.104 --> 1:48:43.812
Do something, master

1:48:43.854 --> 1:48:46.520
'Hit them at least once, master'

1:49:21.062 --> 1:49:24.687
Hey master! This is your fate
every single minute you are here

1:49:24.729 --> 1:49:27.854
Don't think this is the end
There's more to come daily

1:49:27.895 --> 1:49:29.854
We will escape from here tonight

1:49:29.895 --> 1:49:31.520
Try to stop us if you can

1:49:44.604 --> 1:49:46.437
'I was on my bike
sticking to the kerb side'

1:49:46.479 --> 1:49:49.729
Whether he collided by mistake
or deliberately targeted me

1:49:49.770 --> 1:49:51.104
'Only God knows'

1:49:51.145 --> 1:49:52.895
'But his intention is to provoke you'

1:49:52.937 --> 1:49:56.187
Only then you'll get angry and show
your fist power on a handful of boys

1:49:56.229 --> 1:49:59.187
'They will use that as excuse
and pack you off from here'

1:49:59.229 --> 1:50:00.979
'Don't act rashly on impulse'

1:50:02.520 --> 1:50:04.812
Only his leg is fractured
Hand is intact, right?

1:50:09.729 --> 1:50:11.937
[kabaddi-chatter]

1:50:20.520 --> 1:50:23.895
'To love one's own child is common
To love someone else's child is divine'

1:50:27.187 --> 1:50:28.687
Sorry, da

1:50:28.729 --> 1:50:30.770
I couldn't do anything to help you

1:50:30.812 --> 1:50:32.229
It's okay, forget it

1:50:32.270 --> 1:50:33.770
What can you do?

1:50:33.812 --> 1:50:36.854
My fear is those grown up boys are
waiting to pounce on us in kabaddi

1:50:36.895 --> 1:50:39.937
And we have to play against
those beefy buffaloes it seems

1:50:39.979 --> 1:50:41.645
In case we lose...

1:50:41.729 --> 1:50:43.604
...we'll be 'alti'
this entire month

1:50:43.645 --> 1:50:44.770
'Alti' means?

1:50:44.812 --> 1:50:46.729
Being an errand boy

1:50:46.812 --> 1:50:49.729
To be under their beck and call
Do all their dirty jobs like a slave

1:50:49.770 --> 1:50:51.270
I'll anyway lose

1:50:51.311 --> 1:50:54.311
'I am agreeable to being an 'alti'
but they insist I should play, master'

1:50:54.354 --> 1:50:56.229
I snitched to you, right?

1:50:56.270 --> 1:50:58.312
Using kabaddi as an excuse
as if it's just a game

1:50:58.354 --> 1:51:00.354
'...they plan to bash me up, master'

1:51:00.655 --> 1:51:02.072
'Hey Undiyal...!'

1:51:02.645 --> 1:51:03.671
Come, da

1:51:05.687 --> 1:51:06.812
Look here

1:51:06.854 --> 1:51:07.854
Look at me

1:51:07.895 --> 1:51:09.145
'I am calling you...dai!'

1:51:09.187 --> 1:51:11.562
Coming or shall I lift you
and bring you here to play?

1:51:11.604 --> 1:51:13.729
More than the aches
from blows and kicks

1:51:14.104 --> 1:51:16.229
Pain from fear hurts deeper!

1:51:16.559 --> 1:51:18.018
Go with courage, da

1:51:18.601 --> 1:51:20.351
Go and check what he's doing

1:51:20.440 --> 1:51:22.315
Das, he is coming

1:51:47.645 --> 1:51:48.604
Tell me, Madhi

1:51:48.645 --> 1:51:50.687
You snitched about us
to the master, right?

1:51:50.729 --> 1:51:52.354
- Face us now
- Hey!

1:51:52.395 --> 1:51:53.812
I know very well, da

1:51:53.854 --> 1:51:56.312
If Bala plays we will win for sure

1:51:56.395 --> 1:51:58.687
So you got scared and
broke his hand, right?

1:51:58.729 --> 1:52:00.604
Had he been here
would he have defeated us?

1:52:00.645 --> 1:52:03.145
For sure then you would
have lost pathetically

1:52:03.229 --> 1:52:06.062
Call how many ever, whomever,
you want from here to play on your side

1:52:06.104 --> 1:52:08.729
I'll call anyone I want but then
you can't go back on your word

1:52:08.770 --> 1:52:11.687
Call, we won't send you back
without breaking all your teeth today!

1:52:14.312 --> 1:52:16.812
MAAASTER!

1:52:18.229 --> 1:52:20.020
"Clash of wills here"

1:52:21.770 --> 1:52:23.729
"You are ready for your bier"

1:52:25.312 --> 1:52:27.020
[song from 'Ghilli']

1:52:28.854 --> 1:52:32.145
"Kabaddi...kabaddi...do hold your breath"

1:52:32.187 --> 1:52:36.437
"Kabaddi...kabaddi...to show your strength"

1:52:43.395 --> 1:52:45.437
- Tell me, Madhi
- 'I checked the results'

1:52:45.479 --> 1:52:48.312
I am sure all 6 of them
are above 20 years of age

1:52:51.729 --> 1:52:53.562
"Kabaddi...kabaddi...play"

1:52:53.604 --> 1:52:57.062
"On your mark, get set full gear
Sandalwood paste smeared"

1:52:57.145 --> 1:53:00.229
"One foot in the grave, no fear
You are ready for your bier"

1:53:00.270 --> 1:53:01.854
What are you saying?

1:53:01.895 --> 1:53:03.830
Not one of them is less than 18?

1:53:03.882 --> 1:53:06.632
100% sure, in those 6 boys
no one is younger than 18

1:53:12.979 --> 1:53:15.187
"On your mark, get set, ready"

1:53:19.895 --> 1:53:21.812
"Bash them up deadly"

1:53:23.229 --> 1:53:26.270
Master, at least do you know
the name of this game?

1:53:26.312 --> 1:53:28.354
'This is not cricket or football'

1:53:28.395 --> 1:53:30.979
You must hold your breath and
repeat 'kabaddi', you know?

1:53:32.395 --> 1:53:34.020
Our rules are different

1:53:34.062 --> 1:53:35.812
You can't just touch and run

1:53:35.854 --> 1:53:37.895
You must toss your opponent
outside the line

1:53:37.937 --> 1:53:39.729
What...still want to play?

1:53:42.229 --> 1:53:43.520
Come on, da

1:53:56.354 --> 1:53:59.645
"Kabaddi...kabaddi...kabaddi...play"

1:54:06.395 --> 1:54:08.770
Kabaddi...kabaddi...kabaddi

1:54:10.312 --> 1:54:12.229
You're out if you step out of the line

1:54:12.270 --> 1:54:14.395
"On your mark, get set, full gear"

1:54:15.312 --> 1:54:17.229
"Sandalwood paste smeared here"

1:54:17.270 --> 1:54:19.354
'Trying your tricks with us?'

1:54:19.616 --> 1:54:21.491
"You are ready for your tomb"

1:54:22.754 --> 1:54:25.004
"Your downfall is your doom"

1:54:26.687 --> 1:54:28.062
Bingo!

1:54:28.397 --> 1:54:30.022
'He got a solid slap'

1:54:32.400 --> 1:54:34.150
Knock him down

1:54:54.863 --> 1:54:56.280
'He deserves it!'

1:55:00.187 --> 1:55:02.395
- Soooper, master
- Come...face on

1:55:02.479 --> 1:55:03.770
He is hitting us real hard

1:55:03.812 --> 1:55:05.979
If you have the guts
show it now

1:55:06.062 --> 1:55:08.062
Come...come on

1:55:08.301 --> 1:55:11.051
Kabaddi...kabaddi...kabaddi

1:55:12.145 --> 1:55:14.729
Kabaddi...kabaddi...kabaddi

1:55:14.770 --> 1:55:16.062
Lift him

1:55:16.882 --> 1:55:19.340
You dare lay a finger on us
Just you wait and watch!

1:55:20.812 --> 1:55:22.520
Come...come

1:55:26.604 --> 1:55:29.270
How dare you break a boy's hand!

1:55:29.312 --> 1:55:32.062
This is tit for tat time for you

1:55:32.137 --> 1:55:34.429
It hurts, master

1:55:34.489 --> 1:55:36.281
[loud cheering]

1:55:51.965 --> 1:55:54.090
Kabbadi...kabbadi...kabbadi

1:55:58.312 --> 1:56:00.166
"All set to knock you down"

1:56:00.202 --> 1:56:03.494
"Lick your defeat with face on the ground"

1:56:03.597 --> 1:56:07.181
"On your mark, get set, ready to lose"

1:56:07.233 --> 1:56:10.775
"One step to defeat, time for the noose"

1:56:51.708 --> 1:56:55.166
"On your mark, get set, dear
Sandalwood paste smeared"

1:56:55.208 --> 1:56:58.666
"Clash of wills here
Be ready to lie on your bier"

1:56:58.708 --> 1:57:01.249
Kabaddi...kabaddi

1:57:03.981 --> 1:57:05.731
Watch the line

1:57:07.624 --> 1:57:11.333
If you dare lay a finger
on these boys just once more

1:57:12.934 --> 1:57:15.517
"Kabaddi...kabaddi...hold your breath"

1:57:15.581 --> 1:57:20.372
"Kabaddi...show your strength"

1:57:21.083 --> 1:57:22.833
Master?

1:57:23.108 --> 1:57:24.400
Master...?

1:57:24.801 --> 1:57:26.701
- What?
- Is it okay to talk frankly?

1:57:26.736 --> 1:57:29.028
- Camera is recording everything
- Go on, doesn't matter

1:57:29.194 --> 1:57:30.403
I'll tell you, master

1:57:30.467 --> 1:57:32.759
My mother passed away
when I was born

1:57:33.064 --> 1:57:35.314
My neighbor akka raised me

1:57:35.747 --> 1:57:38.747
My father asked that sister
if she will sleep with him!

1:57:38.788 --> 1:57:40.038
That's why

1:57:40.080 --> 1:57:42.288
I threw the grinding stone on his head

1:57:42.325 --> 1:57:44.991
Immediately the police put me in jail

1:57:45.580 --> 1:57:47.997
'That's when I got
trapped with Das anna'

1:57:48.038 --> 1:57:51.288
From then on I had to listen
only to what Das anna says

1:57:53.286 --> 1:57:54.452
Das anna will walk in

1:57:54.493 --> 1:57:57.201
He will check who is addicted to drugs

1:57:57.330 --> 1:58:00.247
Powder, smoke, booze
He will increase the dosage

1:58:01.731 --> 1:58:03.481
Which one of you here

1:58:04.663 --> 1:58:06.330
...has seen Bhavani?

1:58:06.372 --> 1:58:07.747
Bhavani?

1:58:07.788 --> 1:58:09.663
Somehow sounds familiar

1:58:09.705 --> 1:58:11.497
'Where have I heard this name?'

1:58:11.538 --> 1:58:12.538
Master

1:58:12.922 --> 1:58:15.797
We have heard this name
But none of us have seen him

1:58:15.872 --> 1:58:18.270
Das anna is 'be all and end all' here

1:58:18.332 --> 1:58:20.040
We must obey him implicitly

1:58:20.067 --> 1:58:22.775
'If he asks us to surrender
we should do so with our eyes closed'

1:58:22.817 --> 1:58:24.067
Otherwise we will be hanged

1:58:24.124 --> 1:58:25.708
'They recently hanged 2 boys'

1:58:25.740 --> 1:58:27.324
'Didn't you see that, master?'

1:58:28.850 --> 1:58:31.309
Do you all want to go home
and live with your family?

1:58:31.389 --> 1:58:32.973
Or do you want to surrender?

1:58:33.038 --> 1:58:35.580
- Go home, master
- Be with our family

1:58:36.372 --> 1:58:38.163
You have been here for 10 days

1:58:38.205 --> 1:58:40.247
We haven't taken to drugs till now

1:58:40.314 --> 1:58:42.314
Only now we know
our own selves

1:58:43.538 --> 1:58:45.788
'Somehow save us from here, master'

1:58:45.830 --> 1:58:49.622
If you follow what I say, you can
go home and live as you wish

1:58:49.663 --> 1:58:50.747
Will you do as I say?

1:58:50.788 --> 1:58:52.872
- Yes, master
- We will

1:58:52.895 --> 1:58:57.603
Whatever you shared with me now
will you tell the same to the magistrate?

1:58:57.747 --> 1:58:59.705
Of course we will, master

1:58:59.747 --> 1:59:02.372
I'll arrange all the formalities
to get them out on parole

1:59:02.455 --> 1:59:03.348
Thanks, sir

1:59:03.420 --> 1:59:05.670
Let the video evidence
be with Charu till then

1:59:05.759 --> 1:59:07.551
It will reach the magistrate
when you say so

1:59:07.592 --> 1:59:11.176
Master, you shot some video
and cleverly made us confess

1:59:11.233 --> 1:59:13.150
You haven't shared your story

1:59:13.192 --> 1:59:14.525
Tell us
Let's listen

1:59:14.598 --> 1:59:15.639
'Ask him, da'

1:59:15.696 --> 1:59:16.863
Cat got your tongue, huh?

1:59:16.897 --> 1:59:18.772
- Tell us
- Tell us, master

1:59:18.830 --> 1:59:20.413
'Please share your story, master'

1:59:20.473 --> 1:59:22.264
We are asking, right?
Please tell us

1:59:22.330 --> 1:59:25.080
Don't ask for trouble
Trust my voice of experience!

1:59:25.122 --> 1:59:26.913
Wait, they are very eager to hear

1:59:26.955 --> 1:59:28.538
I'll be happy to share
Let them enjoy

1:59:28.580 --> 1:59:30.413
I was in college then

1:59:30.497 --> 1:59:32.372
'I think it was my final year'

1:59:32.413 --> 1:59:35.538
A new teacher joined our college

1:59:35.580 --> 1:59:37.372
Her name was Malar

1:59:37.997 --> 1:59:40.413
Unbelievable one in a million 'Love'

1:59:45.330 --> 1:59:47.830
All of a sudden that girl I loved

1:59:47.872 --> 1:59:49.330
...met with an accident

1:59:49.372 --> 1:59:50.997
'She forgot her past'

1:59:51.038 --> 1:59:53.038
She didn't even know who I was

1:59:53.543 --> 1:59:55.876
She even forgot my mad love for her

1:59:55.920 --> 2:00:00.420
Fate made me attend her wedding
present a bouquet with my own hands!

2:00:01.744 --> 2:00:03.036
After tha-

2:00:04.080 --> 2:00:07.080
Dai! Why are all of you
sniffling and crying?

2:00:07.122 --> 2:00:09.330
Now that girl has totally
forgotten our past

2:00:09.372 --> 2:00:11.830
Master, isn't that teacher Charu akka?

2:00:11.872 --> 2:00:14.497
Hey, this akka is teacher
working as my colleague now

2:00:14.538 --> 2:00:16.372
That was my college time

2:00:16.413 --> 2:00:18.747
Down memory lane
Malar teacher

2:00:18.788 --> 2:00:20.663
Dai, don't you watch Malayalam movies?

2:00:20.705 --> 2:00:22.663
If I don't understand the language

2:00:22.705 --> 2:00:23.913
- I won't watch
- Okay

2:00:23.955 --> 2:00:25.788
Getting late
All of you leave

2:00:25.830 --> 2:00:27.913
Class tomorrow morning as usual

2:00:27.955 --> 2:00:29.580
Okay, master
Bye, master

2:00:29.622 --> 2:00:33.413
How much longer will you quote a film story
if someone asks you about your past life?

2:00:33.455 --> 2:00:36.247
Fool yourself in the bargain
and trick others too?

2:00:36.295 --> 2:00:37.879
Which is a film story?

2:00:38.201 --> 2:00:39.285
Don't act

2:00:39.413 --> 2:00:41.372
What you narrated was
Malayalam film 'Premam'

2:00:41.413 --> 2:00:44.239
Copy cats! They stole my story
and it is released, huh?

2:00:44.295 --> 2:00:46.795
One track mind
on plagiarism, huh?

2:00:47.955 --> 2:00:50.580
Okay, what do you want to know?

2:00:50.622 --> 2:00:51.705
Tell me

2:00:51.747 --> 2:00:53.663
Why did you start drinking?

2:00:54.955 --> 2:00:56.788
Every drunkard will have a story

2:00:56.872 --> 2:00:58.330
Why go into it now?

2:00:58.372 --> 2:00:59.663
If I tell you my reason

2:00:59.705 --> 2:01:03.163
...a handful of them
will follow my footsteps

2:01:04.475 --> 2:01:06.350
Is that necessary?
Isn't it wrong?

2:01:06.497 --> 2:01:07.955
Okay...okay

2:01:08.413 --> 2:01:11.090
I won't tell you now
why I got into this habit

2:01:11.158 --> 2:01:13.741
If you like I'll tell you
why I quit, shall I?

2:01:25.888 --> 2:01:31.138
"When we see those eyes of his
won't love automatically bloom in us?"

2:01:31.179 --> 2:01:36.596
"When we go close to him especially
won't our mind skip like a deer joyfully?"

2:01:37.971 --> 2:01:41.513
"Residing in her heart all the time
His style, his stride so sublime"

2:01:41.554 --> 2:01:47.138
"Featuring in her dreams always
24x7 is his charming dear face"

2:01:48.721 --> 2:01:51.596
"He is Mr Handsome truly
He is our Master, one and only"

2:01:51.638 --> 2:01:54.804
"His smile, not too much, not too less"

2:01:54.888 --> 2:01:59.304
"His charisma beams through in excess"

2:01:59.804 --> 2:02:02.497
"His heart is soft as a flower
Youthfulness is his signature"

2:02:02.548 --> 2:02:05.173
"I pity our girls for sure"

2:02:05.208 --> 2:02:07.833
"His smile is like a sparkler
He's good natured forever"

2:02:07.874 --> 2:02:10.458
"This master with his class
covers one and all en masse"

2:02:10.509 --> 2:02:15.634
"If his fire work-glance falls on you
even a failed heart will pass too"

2:02:15.730 --> 2:02:19.105
"He is single, our news a fact
This is your chance to act"

2:02:19.166 --> 2:02:24.249
"When we see those eyes of his
won't love naturally blossom in us?"

2:02:24.291 --> 2:02:28.999
"When we go close to him especially
won't our mind skip like a deer joyfully?"

2:02:29.041 --> 2:02:31.416
JD is an orphan

2:02:31.458 --> 2:02:33.291
Just grew like a wild tree

2:02:33.333 --> 2:02:34.958
Only after joining this college

2:02:34.999 --> 2:02:36.291
'...he met a professor'

2:02:36.333 --> 2:02:39.416
'His friendship and care
changed JD's life altogether'

2:02:39.458 --> 2:02:40.624
V.C.Selvam!

2:02:40.989 --> 2:02:42.958
But unfortunately he had a health issue

2:02:42.999 --> 2:02:45.124
'He got admitted
in a hospital to get treated-'

2:02:45.166 --> 2:02:46.999
That really shattered JD

2:02:47.083 --> 2:02:49.208
After that he was unable to sleep

2:02:49.249 --> 2:02:52.583
'That damn alcohol took over him'

2:02:52.624 --> 2:02:56.166
"Residing in her heart all the time
His style, his stride so divine"

2:02:56.208 --> 2:03:01.458
"Featuring in her dreams always
24x7 is his endearing dear face"

2:03:03.249 --> 2:03:05.541
"He is Mr Handsome truly
He is our Master, one and only"

2:03:05.583 --> 2:03:09.416
"His smile, not too much, not too less"

2:03:09.458 --> 2:03:12.624
"His charisma beams through in excess"

2:03:14.458 --> 2:03:16.999
"Friendly gaze he sweeps
Calm and collected he speaks"

2:03:17.041 --> 2:03:19.666
"No holds barred at all
All of them flip and fall"

2:03:19.708 --> 2:03:22.708
"Magnetic personality
Quick & slick, sharp is he"

2:03:22.749 --> 2:03:24.958
"Our master is always
Top in all ways"

2:03:24.999 --> 2:03:30.416
"Some kind of innate power he displays
Endearing temerity always in place"

2:03:30.458 --> 2:03:33.833
"If he stands solo; which Miss
won't yearn to be his Mrs?"

2:03:33.874 --> 2:03:37.666
"When we see those eyes of his
won't love naturally blossom in us?"

2:03:37.708 --> 2:03:39.249
What-?

2:03:39.666 --> 2:03:41.208
Please move

2:03:48.083 --> 2:03:49.458
Hey!

2:03:57.416 --> 2:03:58.874
Come on

2:04:08.541 --> 2:04:09.583
Tell me, Charu

2:04:09.624 --> 2:04:10.999
Sir, don't know who they are

2:04:11.041 --> 2:04:13.083
'2 or 3 boys are chasing me'

2:04:13.124 --> 2:04:15.499
Charu, where are you?
Which area?

2:04:15.541 --> 2:04:17.666
In Triplicane, Murugan temple

2:04:17.708 --> 2:04:19.749
Road opposite Murugan temple

2:04:25.958 --> 2:04:27.083
Charu?

2:04:27.833 --> 2:04:29.041
Charu...?

2:04:32.491 --> 2:04:33.741
Follow me

2:04:36.541 --> 2:04:37.749
Damn!

2:04:47.249 --> 2:04:50.583
'They started chasing me when I was
on my way to the magistrate's house'

2:04:50.624 --> 2:04:53.374
I don't know what to do
or where to go

2:04:53.416 --> 2:04:54.666
Charu, don't be scared

2:04:54.708 --> 2:04:55.999
'I will send our boys'

2:04:56.041 --> 2:04:58.958
Go inside some shop there

2:04:59.041 --> 2:05:00.749
'Enter a shop to be safe'

2:05:01.666 --> 2:05:04.166
[TV] 'Thank you for calling, Parandhaman'

2:05:05.291 --> 2:05:07.583
- I've come into a shop, sir
- Turn on the speaker

2:05:07.624 --> 2:05:09.333
What do you need?

2:05:09.374 --> 2:05:11.958
'Bro, 1 minute please
Listen to what I have to say'

2:05:12.874 --> 2:05:14.833
'Let this girl hide
in your shop for a while'

2:05:14.874 --> 2:05:16.291
I'll send my men, please

2:05:16.333 --> 2:05:19.208
My business will get affected
Don't involve me, clear out

2:05:19.249 --> 2:05:21.041
Aren't you a fiery blooded youth?

2:05:21.083 --> 2:05:22.541
'Speak boldly'

2:05:22.624 --> 2:05:24.833
Bro, I'll take care

2:05:24.874 --> 2:05:26.541
- 'You don't worry'
- Thank you, anna

2:05:26.583 --> 2:05:28.416
Come here, dear

2:05:44.499 --> 2:05:46.666
- Did a girl come in here?
- No

2:05:46.749 --> 2:05:50.958
"My dark and bold beau
why was he Uncle Scrooge?"

2:05:51.678 --> 2:05:56.137
"He made my heart soft and cottony
quake with desire; explode in rhapsody"

2:05:56.958 --> 2:06:01.458
"Tell me the auspicious time
when wedding bells will chime?"

2:06:01.499 --> 2:06:04.749
[song from 'Pudhu Nellu Pudhu Naathu']

2:06:04.791 --> 2:06:06.916
- Master, they are teasing m-
- Sshhhhhhhhhh!

2:06:07.541 --> 2:06:11.624
"He made my heart soft and cottony
quake with desire; explode in rhapsody"

2:06:13.642 --> 2:06:15.809
'I told you no one came in here'

2:06:17.041 --> 2:06:18.999
'Bro, where are you going in?'

2:06:19.041 --> 2:06:20.083
'Listen'

2:06:20.124 --> 2:06:21.749
'He already told you no one is here'

2:06:21.791 --> 2:06:23.374
Oldie, shut up

2:06:32.041 --> 2:06:33.624
Give it of your own accord

2:06:33.666 --> 2:06:35.708
Or else just 2 punches
I'll smash your face

2:06:35.749 --> 2:06:37.791
If I have to grab it from you-

2:06:37.833 --> 2:06:39.458
- Dai...dai
- Wait, master

2:06:39.499 --> 2:06:41.083
This face looks familiar

2:06:41.486 --> 2:06:42.694
'Akka'

2:06:43.587 --> 2:06:46.504
'Turn your phone towards him'

2:06:48.777 --> 2:06:49.803
Hey Undiyal...!

2:06:49.853 --> 2:06:51.936
'Hey Button, my dear friend!'

2:06:52.661 --> 2:06:53.749
Undiyal, da

2:06:53.791 --> 2:06:55.541
What are you doing
in this video call?

2:06:55.583 --> 2:06:57.833
Dai, the girl you are chasing is my akka

2:06:57.874 --> 2:06:59.541
- 'Your sister?
- Yes, da'

2:07:00.119 --> 2:07:01.619
I didn't know that

2:07:01.653 --> 2:07:04.458
I was asked to finish her
That's way we chased her

2:07:04.499 --> 2:07:06.749
But tell me, why are you chasing her?

2:07:07.936 --> 2:07:10.186
- What is that?
- She has a camera

2:07:10.787 --> 2:07:12.246
I believe she has a camera

2:07:12.291 --> 2:07:14.624
Ask her to give it
and we'll leave

2:07:14.666 --> 2:07:16.874
Akka, give him what he wants

2:07:16.916 --> 2:07:18.559
We will deal with this differently

2:07:18.619 --> 2:07:19.827
'Okay?'

2:07:20.124 --> 2:07:21.749
'Just give it, akka'

2:07:21.791 --> 2:07:25.416
"My eyes can't close at night
without leaning on your chest in delight"

2:07:30.369 --> 2:07:31.619
'Hey Button'

2:07:32.041 --> 2:07:33.999
I told you she's my akka
I didn't hear your apology?

2:07:34.041 --> 2:07:35.833
- Apologize to her
- Sorry, akka

2:07:35.913 --> 2:07:37.538
'Hey! You boys too'

2:07:37.588 --> 2:07:38.796
Sorry, akka

2:07:39.291 --> 2:07:40.666
Glad you are that scared of me!

2:07:40.747 --> 2:07:43.330
Master, end of incident
Akka safe from any accident

2:07:43.379 --> 2:07:45.379
You talk to her
I'll wait there

2:07:46.161 --> 2:07:48.666
Charu, leave that place immediately

2:07:48.708 --> 2:07:51.916
"Trust us even if we are teeny
For you, we get our hands dirty"

2:07:51.958 --> 2:07:55.916
"We can steal a weapon in jail
Chase you, hot on your trail"

2:07:55.958 --> 2:08:00.249
"Chew a gum for flavor
Take the boys you favor"

2:08:00.291 --> 2:08:02.541
Dai, who are all of you?

2:08:02.936 --> 2:08:04.770
What are you doing?

2:08:04.843 --> 2:08:05.968
Look

2:08:07.004 --> 2:08:08.333
What is this tattoo?

2:08:08.374 --> 2:08:09.499
This branding?

2:08:09.541 --> 2:08:11.041
When boys are sent to this Home

2:08:11.083 --> 2:08:14.124
Das anna will pick up
the sharp ones and train us

2:08:14.166 --> 2:08:17.708
When we get released, he will tattoo
our hand with this Tamil letter 'pa'

2:08:17.749 --> 2:08:20.916
If we show this tattoo in the Mess,
we can eat to our stomach's content

2:08:20.958 --> 2:08:23.416
If you are older, you'll get
plenty of booze and cigarettes

2:08:23.458 --> 2:08:25.583
You can get clothes for free
from their textile shop

2:08:25.666 --> 2:08:28.291
They will even get you
dope from a pharmacy

2:08:29.499 --> 2:08:30.708
But the hitch is

2:08:31.249 --> 2:08:34.666
Every now and then, they will
make us surrender for a crime

2:08:34.804 --> 2:08:37.263
Not to get back into the old
bad ways, I'm staying aloof

2:08:41.916 --> 2:08:44.999
'We have heard this name
But none of us have seen him'

2:08:45.041 --> 2:08:47.208
'Das anna is 'be all and end all' here'

2:08:47.249 --> 2:08:48.874
'We must obey him implicitly'

2:08:48.926 --> 2:08:51.124
- Is it a newly released film?
- 'No one can defy him'

2:08:51.166 --> 2:08:53.499
'He asks us to surrender
we should, with our eyes closed'

2:08:53.541 --> 2:08:55.166
How did you lose track of her?

2:08:55.208 --> 2:08:57.583
Don't know how, Bhavani
I sent only professionals

2:08:57.624 --> 2:08:59.458
- Somehow they messed up-
- Shut up!

2:09:02.747 --> 2:09:04.458
What do we do with this, bro?

2:09:04.499 --> 2:09:08.541
It has a card inside which stores
whatever we shoot or click

2:09:08.614 --> 2:09:11.822
Break that card alone and
keep the camera at my place

2:09:12.083 --> 2:09:13.166
Okay

2:09:13.208 --> 2:09:14.958
When are they announcing the results?

2:09:14.999 --> 2:09:16.791
Heard it's Monday or Tuesday

2:09:16.871 --> 2:09:18.704
You'll anyway win unopposed

2:09:18.754 --> 2:09:20.420
Why should you be tense?

2:09:20.877 --> 2:09:23.335
- I can enjoy, right?
- Yes, then what?

2:09:25.879 --> 2:09:27.004
Sit here

2:09:29.837 --> 2:09:31.462
Do you know this ostrich?

2:09:32.083 --> 2:09:34.416
A bird with a long neck like this

2:09:34.458 --> 2:09:36.416
Have you seen its egg?
It will be this big

2:09:36.458 --> 2:09:38.499
So big in size

2:09:39.481 --> 2:09:42.356
But only that ostrich will know
the pain of hatching such an egg!

2:09:43.541 --> 2:09:45.749
Will you sit here even after
I've explained to you?

2:09:45.791 --> 2:09:47.208
No, Bava

2:09:47.319 --> 2:09:48.944
- Get lost!
- No, Bhavani

2:09:49.999 --> 2:09:52.291
Bhavani, boys want a booze party

2:09:52.333 --> 2:09:53.666
You won't anyway drink

2:09:53.708 --> 2:09:55.083
At least for them-

2:09:56.583 --> 2:09:58.667
Drink to dig your own grave

2:09:58.708 --> 2:10:00.958
- Go ahead
- Thanks a lot, Bhavani

2:10:01.417 --> 2:10:03.333
- 'Goodnight, Bava'
- Goodnight

2:10:07.739 --> 2:10:09.792
Somehow you made me
show you this place

2:10:09.833 --> 2:10:12.083
I was staying away
from this place

2:10:12.150 --> 2:10:13.608
Let's go back, master

2:10:14.465 --> 2:10:16.375
Wait, I have a good reason

2:10:16.417 --> 2:10:17.500
We'll go soon

2:10:17.542 --> 2:10:20.000
'Right, you haven't come here to eat'

2:10:20.042 --> 2:10:24.542
- 'What happened to my chicken 'pakoda'?
- Narayana, serve him fast'

2:10:24.583 --> 2:10:27.542
I thought you were inviting me
for a candle light dinner

2:10:27.583 --> 2:10:29.458
Last time I came here,
there was no power

2:10:29.500 --> 2:10:31.042
They had lit only candles

2:10:33.250 --> 2:10:34.792
Okay, relax

2:10:35.875 --> 2:10:37.875
Don't look at this place

2:10:37.917 --> 2:10:40.208
I heard the food here is super

2:10:41.208 --> 2:10:42.792
'Get a token for the meals'

2:10:43.542 --> 2:10:44.792
'Madam, you too'

2:10:45.583 --> 2:10:47.292
I thought we'll have some privacy

2:10:47.333 --> 2:10:50.917
Close your eyes and
show me your right hand

2:10:51.583 --> 2:10:53.583
- Why?
- Show, I'll tell you

2:10:57.417 --> 2:11:00.250
You shouldn't open your eyes
till I tell you

2:11:02.708 --> 2:11:03.917
'Open now'

2:11:07.042 --> 2:11:09.833
That boy's hand in the salon
had this same mark

2:11:09.875 --> 2:11:11.417
Show this over there

2:11:11.833 --> 2:11:13.583
Ask for 'meals' token

2:11:15.458 --> 2:11:16.750
Why should I-

2:11:16.792 --> 2:11:19.167
All for a good reason
Go and show your hand

2:11:53.208 --> 2:11:54.667
Who the hell is he?

2:12:13.250 --> 2:12:15.583
'We don't differentiate or discriminate'

2:12:16.500 --> 2:12:18.875
'Whoever has a Tamil letter 'pa'
tattooed on their hands...'

2:12:18.917 --> 2:12:21.125
...we give them whatever they ask

2:12:23.917 --> 2:12:26.375
Bhavani's boys will take care of the rest

2:12:37.750 --> 2:12:39.167
What is this for?

2:12:39.250 --> 2:12:41.333
Still some balance left
in my bucket list!

2:13:03.042 --> 2:13:07.833
"Let the drums beat; no restraint
Let the party rock; no constraint"

2:13:07.875 --> 2:13:12.917
"Let our army smash and slam
Our earth will quake with the wham"

2:13:12.958 --> 2:13:17.792
"My hands will never miss a beat
when I beat the drum ever so neat"

2:13:17.833 --> 2:13:21.625
"Even the dormant nerve will dance
hearing my drum's resonance"

2:13:21.667 --> 2:13:22.875
'Beat it!'

2:13:22.917 --> 2:13:27.792
"Till the sun rises to a new day
let the ground shake and sway"

2:13:27.833 --> 2:13:32.750
"Till the game is won, job is done
slow down but have your fun"

2:13:32.792 --> 2:13:36.625
"Even the Lord of Death Yama will die
if he glares with his razor sharp eye"

2:13:36.667 --> 2:13:37.708
'Hey boy!'

2:13:37.750 --> 2:13:41.750
"Light the camphor for our Lord
He is possessed by our demi-god"

2:13:42.220 --> 2:13:47.136
"Look high and low diligently
Every nook & corner and alley"

2:13:47.178 --> 2:13:51.261
"There is no other big gun to defy
Or create a ruckus and vilify"

2:13:51.303 --> 2:13:52.428
'Bhavani!'

2:14:06.053 --> 2:14:08.970
That master is churning in my mind

2:14:09.470 --> 2:14:12.136
Tell him to kill that master
tomorrow before day break

2:14:12.345 --> 2:14:15.886
Why wait till tomorrow morning?
We can close his chapter right now

2:14:18.553 --> 2:14:20.845
Shut your gob
Just do what I say

2:14:23.553 --> 2:14:28.220
"Let the force of his punching fist
make the drumhead rip and split"

2:14:28.261 --> 2:14:32.845
"Let 'sound' listen to the thump and lo!
Announce who struck the blow"

2:14:36.928 --> 2:14:38.053
'You there!'

2:14:38.095 --> 2:14:43.136
"Let the force of his punching fist
make the drumhead rip and split"

2:14:43.178 --> 2:14:47.678
"Let 'sound' listen to the thump and lo!
Announce who struck the blow"

2:14:47.720 --> 2:14:52.220
"Shaking his stupor, without a doubt
he is all set to rip your gut out"

2:14:52.261 --> 2:14:56.678
"To hang you upside down
and skin you alive is his vow"

2:14:56.720 --> 2:14:57.970
'Master...!'

2:15:07.970 --> 2:15:12.803
"Let the drums roll; no restraint
Let festivities begin; no constraint"

2:15:12.845 --> 2:15:17.761
"Let our army smash and slam
Our earth will quake with the wham"

2:15:17.803 --> 2:15:22.678
"My hands will never miss a beat
when I beat the drum; it's a royal treat"

2:15:22.720 --> 2:15:26.303
"Even the dormant nerve will dance
hearing my drum's resonance"

2:15:26.345 --> 2:15:27.636
'Rock & roll'

2:15:27.678 --> 2:15:33.095
"Till the sun rises to a new day
let the ground shake and sway"

2:15:33.428 --> 2:15:35.136
Give me Dinkie Dow if you have

2:15:35.178 --> 2:15:36.636
I don't stock drugs

2:15:37.595 --> 2:15:41.303
"Even the Lord of Death Yama will die
if he glares with his razor sharp eye"

2:15:41.345 --> 2:15:42.470
'Hey boy'

2:15:42.511 --> 2:15:46.720
"Light the camphor for our Lord
He is possessed by our demi-god"

2:16:12.970 --> 2:16:15.470
"Got the man with the plan right here"

2:16:15.511 --> 2:16:18.095
"Bringin' swag with the man right here"

2:16:18.136 --> 2:16:22.178
Forward all the videos
to the police department

2:16:22.220 --> 2:16:25.720
I'll bring the boys
to the Magistrate directly

2:16:26.053 --> 2:16:27.136
Okay

2:16:28.595 --> 2:16:29.678
Master

2:16:30.345 --> 2:16:32.261
This is Bhavani anna's truck

2:16:32.303 --> 2:16:34.803
I've heard he comes here often

2:16:36.553 --> 2:16:37.595
Let's go there

2:16:37.636 --> 2:16:40.136
Aiyaiyo! Are you joking, master?

2:16:40.178 --> 2:16:42.636
I am not coming
You go if you want

2:16:45.970 --> 2:16:49.428
"What existed on earth
even before your birth"

2:16:49.470 --> 2:16:52.345
"Even you can't unearth"

2:16:52.970 --> 2:16:59.303
"What happens after our death?
No clue of the aftermath"

2:17:00.553 --> 2:17:03.928
"As long as we live, to the maximum
let's seize the moment, Carpe Diem"

2:17:03.970 --> 2:17:07.220
"What will we lose in the bargain?"

2:17:07.845 --> 2:17:11.011
"What will we lose and not gain?"

2:17:11.053 --> 2:17:12.845
[song from 'Navarathiri']

2:17:15.345 --> 2:17:18.636
"A whole night of merry-making"

2:17:19.095 --> 2:17:22.095
"The day spent in sleep overtaking"

2:17:22.261 --> 2:17:27.303
"This is the world we rejoice
Reveling in unforbidden joys"

2:17:27.803 --> 2:17:30.011
You move I'll stab you

2:17:30.053 --> 2:17:31.386
Walk straight ahead

2:17:38.553 --> 2:17:41.261
"If He considered it a sin"

2:17:41.303 --> 2:17:42.386
Knock, da

2:17:42.428 --> 2:17:44.928
"Will God create man and woman?"

2:17:46.178 --> 2:17:47.553
To top it all
a secret code!

2:17:47.595 --> 2:17:52.345
"Then why would He tempt them anyway
with a grapevine on the way?"

2:17:54.178 --> 2:17:56.678
If any hand reaches out to his weapon

2:17:57.178 --> 2:17:58.761
He will end up a corpse

2:17:59.136 --> 2:18:00.386
Kneel, man

2:18:01.279 --> 2:18:03.279
- Kneel down
- Switch off the song

2:18:04.345 --> 2:18:06.220
Damn, switch it off!

2:18:08.845 --> 2:18:10.470
Who is Bhavani here?

2:18:11.470 --> 2:18:12.511
Huh?

2:18:13.345 --> 2:18:15.220
Which one of you here
has seen Bhavani?

2:18:31.636 --> 2:18:33.761
What kind of sissy name
is that...Bhavani?

2:18:33.803 --> 2:18:36.553
Was he lying on his stomach
as a baby when he was named?

2:18:40.970 --> 2:18:42.095
Phew!

2:18:43.136 --> 2:18:45.053
Let me make it clear once more

2:18:45.803 --> 2:18:49.095
If any of you do something stupid
trying to retaliate

2:18:49.761 --> 2:18:52.261
I'll sign on your man's
Adam's apple, got it?

2:18:52.845 --> 2:18:54.803
'Try your luck flinging another bottle?'

2:18:55.011 --> 2:18:56.511
That means

2:18:56.886 --> 2:18:59.428
You know Bhavani very well

2:19:01.345 --> 2:19:04.345
Will you go and repeat this
to him verbatim?

2:19:05.553 --> 2:19:07.178
Bhavani...Bhavani

2:19:08.053 --> 2:19:09.803
Bhavani...Bhavani

2:19:11.595 --> 2:19:14.636
A man walked in right royally
knowing it is your den, Bhavani

2:19:15.553 --> 2:19:16.720
Repeat, da

2:19:17.220 --> 2:19:19.053
No, you tell me
I'll convey it

2:19:19.095 --> 2:19:21.803
No, you are scared

2:19:22.803 --> 2:19:25.178
'Listen, I might as well tell all of you'

2:19:25.220 --> 2:19:28.261
The day you killed those 2 boys in
the Observation Home and hung them

2:19:28.345 --> 2:19:30.220
I hung my head in guilt and died

2:19:30.886 --> 2:19:33.136
I'm least bothered about myself hereafter

2:19:33.970 --> 2:19:37.011
Branding those juveniles with a tattoo
and making them do your dirty work

2:19:37.053 --> 2:19:38.595
I've put a full stop to it

2:19:38.845 --> 2:19:42.345
From now on, anyone wants to do anything
using the boys as lambs for the slaughter

2:19:42.386 --> 2:19:44.928
...has to kill me and then go ahead
but that has a slight hitch

2:19:45.803 --> 2:19:49.678
I will kill minimum 10 of you
and only then breathe my last

2:19:50.970 --> 2:19:54.261
Be it Bhavani
or Banumathi!!

2:19:55.845 --> 2:19:57.886
Will you go and tell him
word by word?

2:19:58.511 --> 2:20:00.057
Come, get up

2:20:05.220 --> 2:20:06.470
Close the door

2:20:23.761 --> 2:20:25.345
Who threw that bottle at me, da?

2:20:27.970 --> 2:20:29.011
Come here

2:20:29.053 --> 2:20:30.386
No, Bhavani

2:20:30.428 --> 2:20:32.428
I aimed it at him

2:20:32.553 --> 2:20:35.136
The pen will fall down and
you can escape I thought

2:20:35.178 --> 2:20:36.636
'But it missed and-'

2:20:36.678 --> 2:20:38.595
Hey! Lazy lout
Open the door

2:20:38.845 --> 2:20:39.928
- 'Open the door
- Madcap!'

2:20:39.970 --> 2:20:42.303
- Open the door, da
- What false bravado!

2:20:42.345 --> 2:20:44.303
Son of a scumbag!
Open it, damn you

2:20:44.345 --> 2:20:46.928
Where did you go?
Open now, I'll kill you

2:20:46.970 --> 2:20:48.053
'Hey! Open'

2:20:48.095 --> 2:20:50.303
'How dare you lay a hand
on Bhavani when I'm here?'

2:20:50.345 --> 2:20:51.136
- Kottamuthu
- Come now

2:20:51.178 --> 2:20:53.178
- Hey Kottamuthu
- What did you think of us?

2:20:53.220 --> 2:20:54.970
Bro is calling you

2:20:55.011 --> 2:20:56.011
Come here

2:20:57.810 --> 2:21:00.102
- What are you doing?
- He locked us in

2:21:00.638 --> 2:21:02.720
He was holding a knife
to my neck for an hour

2:21:02.761 --> 2:21:04.178
WTH were you doing then?

2:21:04.220 --> 2:21:06.553
Bhavani, that wasn't a knife

2:21:06.595 --> 2:21:09.011
- It was a pen
- You knew it, huh?

2:21:09.053 --> 2:21:11.970
How will he open the door
if you yell after he has gone?

2:21:12.011 --> 2:21:13.386
Shall we pen him a letter?

2:21:13.428 --> 2:21:15.095
'Sir, please open the door'

2:21:18.595 --> 2:21:20.011
Don't hit me, Bhavani

2:21:27.053 --> 2:21:28.261
Who can draw very well here?

2:21:28.303 --> 2:21:29.928
Master, he is our best artist

2:21:29.970 --> 2:21:33.511
He's the madcap who doodles foul stuff
all over the toilet and the walls, master

2:21:35.511 --> 2:21:36.345
'Hi master'

2:21:36.386 --> 2:21:37.845
I believe you came to my den

2:21:38.178 --> 2:21:41.428
Threatened a man with a pen and
conveyed an important message to Bhavani

2:21:41.470 --> 2:21:42.803
I am that Bhavani

2:21:43.053 --> 2:21:43.928
'Vanakkam'

2:21:43.970 --> 2:21:48.636
If you destroy all that I own,
textile shop, hotel, wine shop

2:21:49.261 --> 2:21:52.553
What the hell will he do?
He is himself a criminal

2:21:52.595 --> 2:21:54.886
'You assumed I won't
go to the police, right?'

2:21:54.928 --> 2:21:56.845
Your assumption is 100% right

2:21:56.886 --> 2:21:58.636
But thinking you'll make
a fool of me was wrong

2:21:58.678 --> 2:22:00.136
'I enquired about you'

2:22:00.178 --> 2:22:02.803
I believe you have a big gang
of ardent fan followers

2:22:02.845 --> 2:22:05.636
'Which one of them can I finish off?
I asked my boys their choice'

2:22:05.678 --> 2:22:08.970
They said we can have a jolly time
killing them all without discrimination

2:22:09.011 --> 2:22:11.886
Let me give you a task
Take a pen and paper'

2:22:11.928 --> 2:22:15.595
List out your favorites
in alphabetical order

2:22:15.636 --> 2:22:17.095
Hey Bhavani!

2:22:17.136 --> 2:22:20.178
Don't ignore girls and kids
thinking I'll be soft on them

2:22:20.220 --> 2:22:22.303
Include their names too definitely

2:22:22.345 --> 2:22:24.595
'Write and call each one of them'

2:22:24.636 --> 2:22:26.595
And then...master?

2:22:26.636 --> 2:22:28.345
- Bro...?
- What happened?

2:22:28.386 --> 2:22:29.720
Give me the phone

2:22:29.761 --> 2:22:30.970
'Hello...?'

2:22:31.011 --> 2:22:33.178
- Why did he hang up on me?
- 'Must have got scared'

2:22:33.220 --> 2:22:34.720
Got very emotional I guess

2:22:35.490 --> 2:22:38.532
Why do emotional men
get so hyper and angry?

2:22:43.720 --> 2:22:46.511
Pick...pick...pick up my call

2:22:46.553 --> 2:22:48.386
[phone ringing]

2:22:51.011 --> 2:22:52.303
Pick up

2:22:52.428 --> 2:22:53.720
- Hi, dude
- Where are you?

2:22:53.761 --> 2:22:55.011
I'm just leaving my office

2:22:55.053 --> 2:22:56.761
- You are safe?
- Yes, what's the problem?

2:22:56.803 --> 2:22:58.636
'Listen to me
Don't step out'

2:22:58.678 --> 2:23:00.511
What is the proble-

2:23:01.178 --> 2:23:02.678
Come on, pick up

2:23:03.303 --> 2:23:04.595
- Sir?
- WHERE ARE YOU?

2:23:04.636 --> 2:23:06.136
- Shut u-
- 'You are safe, right?'

2:23:06.178 --> 2:23:07.845
- 'Yes, sir, what happened?'
- Listen

2:23:07.886 --> 2:23:10.720
Check if our batch students
are safe, okay?

2:23:10.761 --> 2:23:12.303
'Madhi, where is Srinath?'

2:23:12.345 --> 2:23:13.386
'He is here, JD'

2:23:13.428 --> 2:23:14.886
- What is it?
- 'Stay at home, don't go out'

2:23:14.928 --> 2:23:16.053
'Everything safe?'

2:23:16.095 --> 2:23:17.095
JD called me

2:23:17.136 --> 2:23:18.761
'He was so hassled'

2:23:18.803 --> 2:23:20.511
'He told us not to step out'

2:23:20.553 --> 2:23:23.428
Guys, don't step out of your house
Most important, avoid road travel

2:23:23.470 --> 2:23:27.220
'In case you are out, go to any house
or shop nearby or any safe place'

2:23:27.261 --> 2:23:29.678
'JD sir called just now
I think there's a major problem'

2:23:29.720 --> 2:23:30.928
'If you are safe'

2:23:30.970 --> 2:23:33.011
For heaven's sake
text our entire group

2:23:33.053 --> 2:23:34.178
Park the bike

2:23:37.553 --> 2:23:40.011
'Almost everyone in the group
texted they are safe'

2:23:40.053 --> 2:23:42.845
But we couldn't reach
only Bhargav and Savitha, sir

2:23:42.886 --> 2:23:44.720
Don't swerve too much to the right

2:23:44.761 --> 2:23:46.261
Careful!

2:23:49.928 --> 2:23:50.803
Hello?

2:23:50.845 --> 2:23:51.886
I am safe-

2:23:54.845 --> 2:23:55.970
Vanathi, where are you?

2:23:56.011 --> 2:23:57.595
In a mall nearby
What happened?

2:23:57.636 --> 2:23:59.386
- Is Prem with you?
- 'Yes, da'

2:23:59.428 --> 2:24:01.386
He has gone to fetch
my purse from the car-

2:24:03.220 --> 2:24:04.303
'VANATHI, WHAT IS IT?'

2:24:04.345 --> 2:24:05.970
'What happened, Vanathi?'

2:24:06.011 --> 2:24:07.886
'VANATHI, TALK TO ME'

2:24:09.386 --> 2:24:10.553
VANATHI

2:24:11.261 --> 2:24:13.303
- 'Where are you, da?'
- Theater, why, sir?

2:24:13.345 --> 2:24:14.720
- Are you alright?
- What happened?

2:24:14.761 --> 2:24:16.011
SIR...!

2:24:16.053 --> 2:24:17.303
SRI DAI!

2:24:18.220 --> 2:24:19.261
SIR!

2:24:20.511 --> 2:24:21.636
Hey!

2:24:22.720 --> 2:24:24.053
Hey! Get out

2:24:24.095 --> 2:24:25.928
- What happened?
- Savitha, go

2:24:25.970 --> 2:24:27.386
'Bhargav'

2:24:27.428 --> 2:24:29.636
BHARGAV!

2:24:29.678 --> 2:24:30.886
'Bhargav...!'

2:24:31.178 --> 2:24:32.345
'SIR!'

2:24:34.720 --> 2:24:36.053
Sir...!

2:24:38.178 --> 2:24:40.386
Bhargav is dead, sir

2:25:09.678 --> 2:25:11.553
"Got the man with the plan right here"

2:25:11.595 --> 2:25:12.886
"Bringin' swag with the-"

2:25:13.595 --> 2:25:14.886
Master

2:25:15.220 --> 2:25:16.803
How many wickets down?

2:25:17.095 --> 2:25:18.178
'According to the News I got'

2:25:18.220 --> 2:25:19.845
2 wickets down
2 retired hurt

2:25:21.011 --> 2:25:24.220
If you are still stubborn enough
to hang out with that gang

2:25:24.261 --> 2:25:26.053
...you'll lose 4 wickets daily

2:25:26.095 --> 2:25:28.928
'I have never forgiven anyone
who has messed with me till now'

2:25:28.970 --> 2:25:31.178
This is my first time
and I am forgiving you

2:25:31.428 --> 2:25:34.845
Just quit your job, do an 'about turn'
and disappear from this town

2:25:35.470 --> 2:25:38.345
'Otherwise one who escaped today
will die tomorrow and repeat'

2:25:38.386 --> 2:25:40.095
It will go on repeat mode

2:25:40.136 --> 2:25:42.636
They will keep falling like ninepins
Thank you and good bye

2:25:42.678 --> 2:25:44.511
Hey...hey!
Master...master

2:25:44.553 --> 2:25:46.553
'The main reason I called you'

2:25:46.595 --> 2:25:48.886
I didn't lie face down
when I was named it seems

2:25:49.095 --> 2:25:50.720
I was on my back
it was clear as a bell!

2:25:50.761 --> 2:25:52.095
- Hey
- 'Aahn'

2:25:52.136 --> 2:25:53.386
- DAI!
- 'Hahn?'

2:25:55.011 --> 2:25:57.470
I'll dice you, dry and
pickle you to pieces

2:25:58.303 --> 2:25:59.428
Let's lock horns!

2:26:04.095 --> 2:26:06.845
Take care of them just for today

2:26:06.886 --> 2:26:07.886
I'll be back soon

2:26:07.928 --> 2:26:09.261
Don't worry, you go

2:26:09.303 --> 2:26:11.303
'I will ensure the safety of these boys'

2:26:15.136 --> 2:26:17.803
- Aiyo! Let go of me, bro
- Shut up, get into the truck

2:26:17.845 --> 2:26:19.595
- Bro, let go of me
- Hit you

2:26:19.636 --> 2:26:20.803
Where are you taking me?

2:26:20.845 --> 2:26:23.178
- I'm not coming, bro
- Das!

2:26:23.886 --> 2:26:25.095
Hey! Come here

2:26:25.136 --> 2:26:26.636
Das, he's throwing a tantrum

2:26:26.678 --> 2:26:28.803
- Lift him
- Don't force me, bro

2:26:28.845 --> 2:26:30.470
- No...no
- Just listen

2:26:30.511 --> 2:26:32.178
Save me, warden

2:26:32.220 --> 2:26:33.470
Don't do this, Das

2:26:33.511 --> 2:26:35.053
Save us somehow, warden

2:26:35.095 --> 2:26:37.095
- Don't take them
- Let me go, bro

2:26:37.553 --> 2:26:38.636
Move it

2:26:38.678 --> 2:26:42.386
'Hey Das! Where are you taking the boys?'

2:26:47.595 --> 2:26:49.720
[mobile ringing]

2:26:50.053 --> 2:26:52.636
"Bringin' swag with the man right here"

2:26:53.303 --> 2:26:55.678
'Hello, sir
I'm Thulukanam speaking'

2:26:55.720 --> 2:26:58.386
'Das and his boys have
locked us in here'

2:26:58.428 --> 2:27:00.470
'He has taken the boys
who turned approvers'

2:27:00.511 --> 2:27:01.928
'In a truck somewhere, sir'

2:27:01.970 --> 2:27:04.678
'We don't know what to do
Please come soon, sir'

2:27:20.220 --> 2:27:21.720
[mobile ringing]

2:27:22.303 --> 2:27:23.470
Yes, Vanathi

2:27:35.518 --> 2:27:38.065
'This is not the end of the world for us'

2:27:39.053 --> 2:27:41.386
You have gone out of your way
for these boys, enough

2:27:41.428 --> 2:27:44.761
'I have informed the higher authorities
They said they will be here soon'

2:27:45.095 --> 2:27:48.095
"He was chewing betel leaves in bliss
I punched his nose without a miss"

2:27:48.136 --> 2:27:51.261
"You should have seen blood gush out
This Amaran's heart is gold, no doubt"

2:27:51.511 --> 2:27:53.595
[Singing a song from 'Amaran']

2:27:53.636 --> 2:27:56.553
"Just utter the name 'Amaran', bro
soda bottles will fly at our foe"

2:27:56.595 --> 2:27:58.178
I don't care two hoots
about the repercussion

2:27:58.220 --> 2:28:01.011
I'll take full blame
Beat the hell out of them

2:28:01.553 --> 2:28:02.553
Hold this

2:28:03.095 --> 2:28:05.178
"It's a lilting tune anyone can hum"

2:28:05.220 --> 2:28:08.386
"Amaran is a seasoned singer awesome"

2:28:08.428 --> 2:28:11.345
"He was chewing betel leaves in bliss
I punched his nose without a miss"

2:28:11.386 --> 2:28:14.178
"Should have seen his nose bleed
This Amaran's heart is gold indee-"

2:28:14.220 --> 2:28:15.428
Master...master, da

2:28:15.470 --> 2:28:16.553
Back again?

2:28:17.720 --> 2:28:18.928
Hey! Wait...wait

2:28:20.053 --> 2:28:21.303
Plan to hit us?

2:28:21.345 --> 2:28:22.470
Go ahead

2:28:29.678 --> 2:28:30.928
Come here

2:28:32.053 --> 2:28:34.386
Think you've achieved
something great in life

2:28:35.886 --> 2:28:37.345
Shout all you want

2:28:38.553 --> 2:28:39.636
Dai!

2:28:41.053 --> 2:28:42.178
Bhargav

2:28:43.428 --> 2:28:44.845
He is dead, da

2:28:50.095 --> 2:28:53.511
Bhargav created much more trouble
in college than all of you put together

2:28:53.553 --> 2:28:54.678
He is dead now

2:28:55.053 --> 2:29:00.345
If a real rowdy reforms and just when
he wants to lead a good life, if he dies-

2:29:00.511 --> 2:29:02.636
Do you know it is
the height of cruelty?

2:29:02.803 --> 2:29:05.636
The faith people around him have,
to turn over a new leaf will vanish

2:29:05.678 --> 2:29:07.011
Oh my gawd!

2:29:07.261 --> 2:29:09.136
Master has started preaching to us

2:29:09.178 --> 2:29:10.220
Ignore them, bro

2:29:10.261 --> 2:29:12.595
Why do you treat them
on an equal footing with you?

2:29:12.636 --> 2:29:14.261
These mongrels won't reform
even if they die!

2:29:14.303 --> 2:29:16.261
Yov! Who will reform?

2:29:16.928 --> 2:29:19.386
When have we treated him with respect?

2:29:19.428 --> 2:29:21.803
Or given him time, place
or an opportunity to reform?

2:29:22.553 --> 2:29:25.553
Undiyal, Odacha Kadalai, Bottle Mani,
Soda Sekar, what kind of names?

2:29:25.595 --> 2:29:28.595
Then how will they remember
their family or tender love and care?

2:29:29.428 --> 2:29:31.345
Family and society alienate them

2:29:31.386 --> 2:29:33.678
If everybody has exiled him
how will he reform?

2:29:36.470 --> 2:29:37.636
Come here, da

2:29:37.970 --> 2:29:39.053
What?

2:29:39.845 --> 2:29:43.095
1st crime by many boys here
is based on emotion quotient

2:29:43.761 --> 2:29:45.886
Affection, betrayal, anger,
or a rush of adrenalin

2:29:45.928 --> 2:29:47.261
Each with a reason

2:29:48.220 --> 2:29:49.470
But after the first time

2:29:49.511 --> 2:29:53.678
You know what instigates you to commit
every crime you pile on to your account?

2:29:54.303 --> 2:29:55.553
Intoxication!

2:29:58.345 --> 2:30:00.136
I can bet on this, da

2:30:00.553 --> 2:30:03.720
All other crimes after your 1st was
committed losing control of your senses

2:30:03.761 --> 2:30:05.886
Didn't you booze?
Didn't you have a ball?

2:30:06.011 --> 2:30:07.386
Oh! Yes, sir

2:30:07.428 --> 2:30:08.595
Open your warped mind!

2:30:08.862 --> 2:30:11.321
Only a drunkard can talk
of how it ruined his family

2:30:11.636 --> 2:30:13.345
Only because of my addiction

2:30:14.303 --> 2:30:16.928
2 boys lost their lives
I got that into my thick head

2:30:17.303 --> 2:30:18.220
I quit drinking

2:30:18.261 --> 2:30:21.053
'Chee! Don't be a drama king, master!'

2:30:21.095 --> 2:30:22.428
Am I brewing liquor at home?

2:30:22.511 --> 2:30:24.178
Blaming the buyer
instead of the seller!

2:30:24.220 --> 2:30:27.720
That's exactly what I'm saying
This intoxication is a political game

2:30:28.761 --> 2:30:31.220
You are not yet 18 years
You can't watch this Adult film

2:30:31.261 --> 2:30:33.553
A security guard stands out
to push you out, right?

2:30:33.636 --> 2:30:35.928
Why is no one standing guard
outside a wine shop?

2:30:35.970 --> 2:30:39.595
How do 10 -15 year olds get hold
of a booze bottle and cigarette?

2:30:40.970 --> 2:30:42.470
Politics

2:30:44.053 --> 2:30:46.886
Bhavani is moving his pawn
and playing this kind of politics

2:30:47.220 --> 2:30:49.428
When the law is against child labor

2:30:49.470 --> 2:30:52.636
...that beast is forcing the same boys
into nefarious activities unwillingly

2:30:56.803 --> 2:30:58.011
What is this?

2:30:58.524 --> 2:30:59.690
What is it?

2:30:59.886 --> 2:31:02.595
Like bribing you to vote and
you end up with an inked finger

2:31:02.636 --> 2:31:05.595
He gives you freebies and
brands you with a tattoo

2:31:06.595 --> 2:31:10.553
He has bathed you in basic amenities
providing free food and clothing

2:31:13.303 --> 2:31:14.803
Good lord!

2:31:16.386 --> 2:31:17.636
Enough of this atrocity

2:31:18.261 --> 2:31:22.386
You have packed those boys who believed
they have a good future into that truck

2:31:23.761 --> 2:31:26.678
Don't know if they will hang from a fan
or be run over by a tyre

2:31:27.720 --> 2:31:28.761
But

2:31:29.636 --> 2:31:31.178
I will save them

2:31:31.636 --> 2:31:33.428
Every single one of them

2:31:39.845 --> 2:31:41.261
What did he say, da?

2:31:41.720 --> 2:31:44.053
He will kill all those who like me?

2:31:44.386 --> 2:31:45.456
Hey!

2:31:45.517 --> 2:31:47.267
[ironical laughter]

2:31:48.386 --> 2:31:51.220
There are zillions outside who like me
Mind, body, heart and soul, da

2:31:54.095 --> 2:31:55.845
Ask him to try his luck

2:31:59.386 --> 2:32:05.303
'Bro, Bhavani has loaded the documents,
money bags of his 'benamis' in his lorries'

2:32:05.345 --> 2:32:07.886
'He is planning to
cross the border tonight'

2:32:08.345 --> 2:32:10.428
'The boys are in one of the trucks, bro'

2:32:21.345 --> 2:32:22.553
Bhavani

2:32:22.595 --> 2:32:24.511
All 40 lorries have crossed the border

2:32:24.553 --> 2:32:26.011
Expected anytime now

2:32:26.886 --> 2:32:28.220
Those boys?

2:32:28.386 --> 2:32:30.803
Das is bringing them in the container

2:33:57.761 --> 2:33:58.845
Go

2:34:35.511 --> 2:34:36.761
Finish her off!

2:34:39.779 --> 2:34:41.196
Vanathi...Vanathi

2:34:44.220 --> 2:34:45.720
Run over her

2:34:46.470 --> 2:34:47.511
Vanathi

2:34:55.011 --> 2:34:56.553
Vanathi, take the wheel

2:36:09.511 --> 2:36:11.220
Come...come

2:36:47.011 --> 2:36:48.636
Bang his car and kill them

2:37:07.553 --> 2:37:09.178
Come...come

2:37:09.720 --> 2:37:10.970
'Stop...stop'

2:37:12.386 --> 2:37:15.261
If those 15 boys turn approvers
whom will they point their fingers at?

2:37:15.303 --> 2:37:16.261
Das of course

2:37:16.303 --> 2:37:18.345
They have never met you, Bhavani

2:37:18.386 --> 2:37:20.220
What if Das turns approver?

2:37:26.521 --> 2:37:27.970
Your name, Bhavani

2:37:28.011 --> 2:37:29.636
Then kill Das

2:37:54.428 --> 2:37:55.470
Go

2:37:55.511 --> 2:37:56.595
Go, da

2:37:57.886 --> 2:38:00.178
Do you want him to kill me
out of your sight?

2:38:00.220 --> 2:38:01.761
Your words came to my mind

2:38:02.345 --> 2:38:04.470
'I will give my life for you'

2:38:05.220 --> 2:38:06.386
Give it now

2:38:09.386 --> 2:38:11.636
I thought of you
as my own elder brother

2:38:12.220 --> 2:38:13.928
I regarded you as my anna

2:38:14.136 --> 2:38:16.761
Even I thought of you
as my very own younger brother

2:38:16.928 --> 2:38:18.303
'What do you want me to do?'

2:38:18.345 --> 2:38:19.636
Where are the boys?

2:38:20.761 --> 2:38:22.303
Where are they, da?

2:38:23.159 --> 2:38:25.909
Hey! Go and check the container

2:38:27.845 --> 2:38:29.553
Go...move it

2:38:47.470 --> 2:38:48.720
Let's see who wins
You or me?

2:38:48.761 --> 2:38:50.261
Das, listen to me

2:38:50.303 --> 2:38:52.220
Listen to me
JUST LISTEN!

2:38:53.470 --> 2:38:54.553
Hear me out

2:38:55.178 --> 2:38:58.761
Oral statement by all those boys
point fingers accusingly only at you

2:38:59.303 --> 2:39:02.095
They don't even know the name Bhavani

2:39:02.136 --> 2:39:03.428
Bhavani knows that too

2:39:03.470 --> 2:39:04.886
Give it serious thought

2:39:04.928 --> 2:39:06.803
Will he kill all the boys?

2:39:06.845 --> 2:39:09.907
Or kill the one they are pointing
fingers at, which is YOU?

2:39:09.967 --> 2:39:12.634
In one swift blow-

2:39:14.714 --> 2:39:16.256
That is not my intention

2:39:16.709 --> 2:39:19.167
Let's stop with the lives already lost

2:39:19.761 --> 2:39:21.678
I'm saying this like a broken record

2:39:21.720 --> 2:39:22.761
Bhavani is clever

2:39:22.803 --> 2:39:25.553
He won't kill the boys
His target is YOU

2:39:26.428 --> 2:39:28.636
Listen to me once
Only this time

2:39:28.678 --> 2:39:32.178
Ask him if you can bring the boys
in front of him he will say 'no'

2:39:32.345 --> 2:39:33.511
Continue to ask repeatedly

2:39:33.553 --> 2:39:35.803
You'll know the true colors of Bhavani

2:39:36.428 --> 2:39:38.011
If this doesn't happen-

2:39:40.345 --> 2:39:42.136
I am all yours to kill

2:41:34.386 --> 2:41:36.303
"Oooooh yeah"

2:41:36.345 --> 2:41:38.095
"Master"

2:41:38.428 --> 2:41:40.470
"They call me...master"

2:41:41.303 --> 2:41:43.261
"You know me...master"

2:41:44.595 --> 2:41:46.178
"I am master the blaster"

2:41:46.220 --> 2:41:47.678
"Ooooooh yeah!"

2:41:47.720 --> 2:41:48.970
"Master"

2:41:49.845 --> 2:41:51.511
"They call me...master"

2:41:53.928 --> 2:41:55.011
Welcome, master

2:41:57.330 --> 2:41:59.580
This is the first time
Real face to face, right?

2:42:03.857 --> 2:42:06.107
Loaded with emotion, huh?

2:42:07.096 --> 2:42:08.305
My dear master

2:42:10.962 --> 2:42:13.003
Bhavani isn't just a name

2:42:13.979 --> 2:42:16.146
It's a kingdom I created for myself

2:42:16.462 --> 2:42:19.670
You can't create a world record
with your overnight lesson

2:42:20.295 --> 2:42:23.462
If he was sharing his pearls of wisdom
what about the mud between your ears?

2:42:25.878 --> 2:42:27.670
You carried that boy on your waist?

2:42:28.397 --> 2:42:30.230
Did you think they are kids?

2:42:31.438 --> 2:42:33.271
They are killers of the worst kind

2:42:35.605 --> 2:42:37.605
I've already given you too much time

2:42:37.638 --> 2:42:39.305
Still I'll give you 2 minutes

2:42:39.815 --> 2:42:42.149
If you can ki-

2:42:44.058 --> 2:42:46.225
Master, why did you hit me in mid speech?

2:42:46.259 --> 2:42:47.759
Didn't you ask for it?

2:42:48.511 --> 2:42:49.595
Come

2:42:49.768 --> 2:42:51.893
Is this all the force you can muster?

2:44:06.553 --> 2:44:07.678
Master

2:44:47.761 --> 2:44:49.720
[fired up laughter]

2:45:21.470 --> 2:45:22.761
Master!

2:45:22.803 --> 2:45:24.803
Get up, master

2:45:26.373 --> 2:45:27.665
Job done and dusted

2:45:29.428 --> 2:45:31.261
'Lord, pardon this sinner'

2:45:37.339 --> 2:45:38.631
Don't!

2:45:41.126 --> 2:45:44.501
Hey! I am fighting here for your sake

2:45:45.261 --> 2:45:48.178
So your hands don't grip
a knife once more

2:45:48.636 --> 2:45:50.011
Your mind

2:45:50.053 --> 2:45:52.386
Your mind should not
go back to its old way

2:45:52.428 --> 2:45:53.886
I am fighting your cause

2:45:53.928 --> 2:45:55.303
Not one of you

2:45:55.845 --> 2:45:58.053
Not even one of you
should raise your hand

2:45:59.470 --> 2:46:00.636
Step back

2:46:02.534 --> 2:46:03.701
MOVE BACK!

2:46:07.573 --> 2:46:12.490
"O master, come to my den
If you don't, I'll force you then"

2:46:13.345 --> 2:46:15.553
[singing a popular song from 'Bommalattam']

2:46:15.636 --> 2:46:17.928
"In my own hot spot
you bet I'm a big shot"

2:46:18.803 --> 2:46:20.345
'How was it?'

2:46:20.508 --> 2:46:22.841
You're teaching a lesson
even when you're about to die

2:46:22.883 --> 2:46:24.341
Is this your last lesson, master?

2:46:25.550 --> 2:46:26.717
'Come'

2:47:04.345 --> 2:47:06.178
Shall we have it this way?

2:47:15.511 --> 2:47:17.011
Show me your fist power

2:47:35.011 --> 2:47:36.636
[whistling]

2:48:08.511 --> 2:48:10.178
- Hey...hey
- Master

2:48:10.428 --> 2:48:13.220
- Take the boys to the truck
- Okay, master

2:48:13.261 --> 2:48:14.470
Hey Das

2:48:42.511 --> 2:48:44.011
'Vaathi...!'

2:48:50.034 --> 2:48:53.409
"Come, my dear dude
Raw banana 'bajji' for you"

2:48:53.470 --> 2:48:56.553
"I will tear your body to tatters
Fry and serve as golden fritters"

2:48:56.595 --> 2:48:59.636
[song from the film 'Thangaikor Geetham']

2:48:59.678 --> 2:49:02.970
"I will tear your body in a jiffy
Fry and serve as bajji"

2:49:25.182 --> 2:49:26.682
Master...master...wait

2:49:29.136 --> 2:49:30.845
Sit down

2:49:35.845 --> 2:49:37.136
Master

2:49:38.384 --> 2:49:40.884
A problem won't be solved
by killing a person

2:49:40.932 --> 2:49:43.141
I asked a man
when I was just 17

2:49:43.650 --> 2:49:45.900
This is the same request
I'm asking you

2:49:46.310 --> 2:49:48.102
Let me live

2:49:49.065 --> 2:49:50.815
I will do anything for you

2:49:51.170 --> 2:49:52.845
I won't harm those boys

2:49:52.971 --> 2:49:56.055
You are the one who made
those innocent children criminals

2:49:57.600 --> 2:49:58.850
One-

2:49:59.857 --> 2:50:01.803
Only 1 year

2:50:01.967 --> 2:50:05.907
You were let into that Observation Home
and you've progressed so much in life

2:50:05.948 --> 2:50:09.657
If you are punished and sent to jail
imagine what you'll do to this town

2:50:15.467 --> 2:50:17.092
I'll get into politics

2:50:18.196 --> 2:50:19.654
I'll start a party

2:50:20.357 --> 2:50:22.149
Will you join me?

2:50:22.863 --> 2:50:24.155
Master

2:50:25.423 --> 2:50:26.506
What?

2:50:26.696 --> 2:50:28.404
Sssshhhhhh!

2:50:51.263 --> 2:50:53.636
[appeased laughter]

2:50:54.920 --> 2:50:56.920
Job done, dusted, dunzo!

2:50:58.951 --> 2:51:00.868
[victorious laughter]

2:51:01.740 --> 2:51:06.323
"Let me sing a 'kutti' story
Pay attention, listen to me"

2:51:07.974 --> 2:51:12.391
"If you want, take it or else
no need tension, leave it, baby"

2:51:14.084 --> 2:51:17.261
"Life is very short, nanba"

2:51:17.303 --> 2:51:19.178
- Master
- Who is that?

2:51:21.034 --> 2:51:22.868
The boys are in the truck, master

2:51:24.391 --> 2:51:26.307
Come here
Sit down

2:51:27.595 --> 2:51:28.636
Sit

2:51:33.986 --> 2:51:36.236
Shall I surrender instead of you?

2:51:38.182 --> 2:51:40.724
Won't you understand till the very end?

2:51:40.970 --> 2:51:44.261
Each person has to endure
the punishment according to his crime

2:51:45.178 --> 2:51:46.220
Madcap!

2:51:46.261 --> 2:51:48.318
I feel I should do something for you

2:51:48.381 --> 2:51:51.298
Tell me if you have a family
I'll take care of them till you're back

2:51:53.097 --> 2:51:56.347
I overheard the children in the reformatory
saying you loved a girl it seems

2:51:57.088 --> 2:51:59.672
A girl from an affluent family
Already engaged to someone

2:52:00.349 --> 2:52:02.182
Shall I go and talk to her?

2:52:03.876 --> 2:52:05.792
Maybe I can share my epic story!

2:52:05.865 --> 2:52:08.073
Listen, my dear boy

2:52:08.678 --> 2:52:10.553
My name was not JD then

2:52:10.888 --> 2:52:12.221
Jack Daniels

2:52:12.673 --> 2:52:15.006
People called me 'Jack'

2:52:15.506 --> 2:52:16.803
I used to draw well

2:52:16.845 --> 2:52:18.428
Good at a game of cards

2:52:18.970 --> 2:52:23.178
In such a game we were lucky
My friend and I won 2 tickets

2:52:24.123 --> 2:52:27.415
You would have seen everyone
run to catch a bus or train

2:52:27.803 --> 2:52:31.261
But imagine we ran and caught a ship
about to leave the dock

2:52:31.751 --> 2:52:33.084
Hahn?

2:52:33.595 --> 2:52:36.470
That's where I set eyes on her
for the very 1st time

2:52:36.636 --> 2:52:38.470
Her name was Rose

2:52:40.345 --> 2:52:42.053
What did you say her name was?

2:52:42.970 --> 2:52:44.053
Rose

2:52:44.220 --> 2:52:45.970
Rose...Jack

2:52:46.011 --> 2:52:47.595
Listen to my love story

2:52:47.636 --> 2:52:50.053
After I fell head over heels
in love with her, I found out

2:52:50.095 --> 2:52:52.011
...she's already engaged

2:52:53.053 --> 2:52:55.928
After that, as we were sailing smoothly

2:52:55.970 --> 2:52:58.178
The ship hit an iceberg on the way?

2:52:59.525 --> 2:53:00.608
How do you know that?

2:53:00.657 --> 2:53:02.323
I'll wait outside, master

2:53:02.380 --> 2:53:05.338
- Listen to my full epic love story
- No need, it's okay, master

2:53:07.607 --> 2:53:11.178
'Since manipulation of boys into crimes
by anti social elements was proved'

2:53:11.220 --> 2:53:12.970
'With the aid of proper evidence'

2:53:13.011 --> 2:53:15.386
'That specific Govt Reformatory
was shut down permanently'

2:53:15.428 --> 2:53:19.720
'Of the 63 inmates, those above 18
were sent to Central Prison'

2:53:19.761 --> 2:53:23.553
'And those below 18 were sent
to other Govt reformatories'

2:53:24.172 --> 2:53:25.672
Your fingerprint over there

2:53:27.915 --> 2:53:28.975
Go inside

2:53:35.623 --> 2:53:37.873
What is the crime you are serving term for?

2:53:38.415 --> 2:53:41.582
Baby face, partner
Must be a gigolo

2:53:41.623 --> 2:53:43.915
Look at his face
Like a parcel folded into four

2:53:43.957 --> 2:53:47.082
Juveniles of Nagercoil
in that Bhavani case

2:53:47.373 --> 2:53:49.582
I heard it was 7 of them
Only 6 are here

2:53:49.623 --> 2:53:52.457
Baby face is here
Handsome face is missing

2:53:52.498 --> 2:53:53.701
Where is your master?

2:53:53.758 --> 2:53:56.091
Must have been sent to Vellore jail

2:54:01.582 --> 2:54:03.115
It's even more convenient, partner

2:54:03.167 --> 2:54:05.708
We go to Vellore in 10 days
We'll finish him there

2:54:05.789 --> 2:54:08.289
Then we will meet your master in Vellore

2:54:11.207 --> 2:54:12.665
Transfer only after 10 days, huh?

2:54:12.707 --> 2:54:14.748
- Are you here till then?
- Why?

2:54:14.790 --> 2:54:16.388
Drag that 'beedi'
deep into your lungs

2:54:16.441 --> 2:54:18.441
This is the last 'beedi' you'll smoke

2:54:19.040 --> 2:54:20.582
Over dramatic punch line!

2:54:20.623 --> 2:54:22.582
You're teaching ME
about the 'prisoner'!!

2:54:22.915 --> 2:54:24.670
You would have seen
notorious prisoners

2:54:24.712 --> 2:54:26.212
But guess who is coming now

2:54:26.433 --> 2:54:27.558
MASTER

2:54:27.591 --> 2:54:28.633
"Master coming!"

2:54:28.667 --> 2:54:29.792
"Move aside!"

2:54:34.516 --> 2:54:36.141
"Be safe and safeguarded!"

2:54:57.415 --> 2:55:00.207
subtitled by rekhs
assisted by harini

2:55:02.508 --> 2:55:06.133
"The second our commander steps in
it's like an atom bomb exploding"

2:55:19.950 --> 2:55:21.034
"Master coming!"

2:55:21.091 --> 2:55:22.341
"Move aside!"

2:55:26.540 --> 2:55:28.040
'Rock & roll!'

2:55:33.082 --> 2:55:36.149
"Deliberately if you make trouble"

2:55:36.207 --> 2:55:38.998
"It will boomerang on you centuple"

2:55:39.040 --> 2:55:41.748
"If you jeer or sneer at us"

2:55:41.790 --> 2:55:44.498
"Mind you, you'll be limbless"

2:55:49.457 --> 2:55:50.582
Aiyo!

2:55:54.832 --> 2:55:56.665
"Tell topsy turvy
Yell curvy scurvy"

2:56:17.415 --> 2:56:19.957
"Tear them to tatters
Scare them to scatter"

